baby.%20She%20decided%20it%20was%20time%20to%20retire%20her%20sex%20education%20channel%2C%20where%20she%20has%20over%20700%2C000%20followers%2C%20after%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot%20of%20soul%20searching.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20knew%20something%20needed%20to%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BI%20could%20feel%20I%20was%20close%20to%20burnout%2C%20I%20wasn't%20feeling%20motivated%2C%20and%20things%20were%20becoming%20financially%20unsustainable%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I%20didn't%20know%20what%20to%20change.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20decided%20to%20say%20goodbye%20to%20her%20main%20channel%20and%20her%20sex%20education%20podcast%20%26quot%3BDoing%20It%26quot%3B%20in%20favor%20of%20more%20parenting%20content%20on%20her%20second%2C%20smaller%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20decade%20is%20a%20long%20time%20to%20be%20doing%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20in%20other%20careers%2C%20it's%20totally%20normal%20to%20move%20on%20and%20change%20what%20you're%20doing%20after%20you've%20been%20in%20it%20for%20so%20many%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221271%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hannah%20Witton%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e4e52f0bb2ebc49c35da382%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22673%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHannah%20Witton%20has%20closed%20down%20her%20sex%20education%20channel%20which%20she%20started%20in%202013.%3Cp%3EHannah%20Witton%20%2F%20YouTube%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EScaling%20up%20in%20an%20AI%20world%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWitton%20said%20she's%20always%20been%20aware%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bgrowth%20trap%26quot%3B%20creators%20can%20fall%20into.%20When%20they%20find%20success%2C%20the%20logical%20step%20is%20to%20%26quot%3Bscale%20up%26quot%3B%20with%20more%20channels%2C%20businesses%2C%20and%20responsibilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20can%20be%20great%2C%20Witton%20said%2C%20but%20it%20turns%20creators%20into%20m