uster%20%3Cem%3E3%20Idiots%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20observing%20a%2021-day%20fast%2C%20amid%20freezing%20temperatures%2C%20to%20press%20for%20the%20Union%20Territory%E2%80%99s%20special%20status%20under%20the%20sixth%20schedule%20of%20the%20constitution%20of%20India%20and%20statehood.%20These%20demands%20have%20dominated%20the%20politics%20of%20the%20region%20after%20Ladakh%20was%20dismembered%20from%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20granted%20a%20Union%20Territory%20status%20in%202019%20by%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party-led%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20started%20the%20fast%20on%20March%206%20after%20parleys%20between%20leadership%20of%20Ladakh%20and%20Union%20home%20ministry%20reached%20a%20dead-end%20with%20the%20Apex%20Body%20Leh%20(ABL)%20and%20Kargil%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(KDA)%20saying%20that%20the%20sub-committee%20level%20talks%20and%20their%20separate%20meeting%20with%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20didn%E2%80%99t%20yield%20any%20concrete%20and%20positive%20outcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20over%20phone%20from%20the%20venue%20of%20his%20hunger%20strike%2C%20Wangchuk%2C%20who%20entered%20the%207th%20day%20of%20his%20strike%20today%2C%20said%20that%20Ladakhis%20are%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20dejected%2C%20disappointed%20and%20frustrated%E2%80%9D%20due%20to%20the%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20approach%20to%20their%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20government%20has%20been%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20careless%20and%20insensitive%E2%80%9D%20towards%20genuine%20demands%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20set-up%20a%20bad%20precedent%20of%20distrust%20for%20the%20entire%20nation%20for%20decades%20to%20come.%20You%20can%20make%20any%20promise%20and%20get%20away%20with%20it.%20Electoral%20promises%20and%20manifestos%20will%20have%20no%20meaning%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWangchuk%20was%20referring%20to%20the%20promises%20made%20by%20BJP%20regarding%20inclusion%20of%20Ladakh%20in%20the%20sixth%20schedule%20of%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNot%20only%20once%2C%20they%20made%20the%20same%20promise%20twice.%20In%202019%2C%20it%20was%20among%20their%20top%20three%20promises%20and%20in%202020%20Hill%20Council%20polls%2C%20it%20was%20their%20topmost%20promise%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sixth%20schedule%20provides%20for%20the%20administration%20of%20certain%20tribal%20areas%20as%20autonomous%20entities.%20It%20allows%20creation%20of%20autonomous%20district%20councils%20and%20regional%20councils%20endowed%20with%20certain%20legislative%2C%20executive%2C%20judicial%20and%20financial%20powers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20videos%20on%20social%20media%2C%20Wangchuk%C2%A0has%20been%20seeking%20special%20status%20for%20the%20region%20to%20safeguard%20its%20fragile%20environs%20and%20glaciers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20asked%20that%20certain%20quarters%20are%20citing%20the%20small%20size%20of%20Ladakh%E2%80%99s%20population%20to%20oppose%20its%20demand%20for%20statehood%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20Sikkim%20became%20a%20state%2C%20it%20had%20roughly%202.50%20lakh%20population%20and%20Ladakh%20today%20has%20three%20lakh%20population.%20When%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20intentions%20are%20right%2C%20they%20can%20do%20things%20and%20when%20it%20is%20not%2C%20they%20can%20get%20away%20with%20excuses.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Ladakhis%20now%20feel%20it%20is%20like%20a%20colony%20and%20commissioners%20from%20some%20faraway%20places%20come%20and%20govern%20them.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20no%20democracy%2C%20no%20voting%20rights%20to%20elect%20their%20representatives%20to%20an%20Assembly.%20It%20is%20like%20a%20colony%20in%20the%20olden%20times%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWangchuk%20said%20that%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20mobilise%20people%20in%20Ladakh%2C%20and%20in%20the%20nation%2C%20to%20express%20their%20opinion%2C%20maybe%20through%20the%20electoral%20process%20in%20the%20upcoming%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20will%20calmly%20elect%20the%20right%20people%20and%20reject%20the%20wrong%20parties%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20when%20asked%20whether%20Ladakhis%20would%20express%20their%20anger%20against%20the%20Union%20government%20over%20these%20demands%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20he%20is%20touched%20by%20the%20bonhomie%20between%20people%20of%20Leh%20and%20Kargil%20over%20these%20serious%20issues%20which%20have%20far-reaching%20effects%20for%20a%20longtime%20to%20come.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20sad%20incident%20has%20some%20positive%20aspects.%20The%20people%20have%20united%20and%20resolved%20their%20differences%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Buddhist-majority%20Leh%20and%20Muslim-majority%20Kargil%20have%20been%20arch-rivals%20in%20the%20past%2C%20but%20they%20have%20come%20together%20to%20fight%20for%20sixth%20schedule%20and%20statehood%20for%20the%20Union%20Territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20Sonam%20Wangchuk%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFifty-seven-year-old%20Sonam%20Wangchuk%20is%20an%20engineer%2C%20innovator%20and%20education%20reformist.%20He%20is%20the%20founding-director%20of%20the%20Students%E2%80%99%20Educational%20and%20Cultural%20Movement%20of%20Ladakh%20founded%20in%201988.%20Wangchuk%20was%20instrumental%20in%20the%20launch%20of%20operation%20New%20Hope%20in%201994%2C%20a%20collaboration%20of%20government%2C%20village%20communities%20and%20civil%20society%20to%20bring%20reforms%20in%20the%20government%20school%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20he%20was%20conferred%20with%20the%20Ramon%20Magsaysay%20Award%20for%20his%20efforts%20to%20develop%20educational%20reform%20programmes%20that%20focus%20on%20%E2%80%9Ccreative%2C%20child-friendly%2C%20and%20activity-based%E2%80%9D%20education%20in%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%