re%20a%20%E2%80%98party%20with%20a%20difference%2C%E2%80%99%20the%20newly%20re-born%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20used%20to%20boast%20during%20the%20%E2%80%9880s%20and%20%E2%80%9890s.%20The%20tag%20line%2C%20coined%20by%20K.R.%20Malkani%2C%20was%2C%20to%20an%20extent%2C%20apt.%20Those%20were%20the%20days%20when%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20organisational%20bodies%20met%20at%20regular%20interval%20while%20the%20ruling%20party%20Congress%20followed%20the%20high%20command%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20organisational%20bodies%20held%20free%20and%20fair%20discussions%20within%20the%20ideological%20framework%20of%20the%20RSS.%20The%20National%20Executive%20(NE)%20had%20quarterly%20meetings%20held%20at%20different%20state%20capitals.%20At%20the%20National%20Council%20meeting%20%E2%80%93%20a%20three-day%20jamboree%20open%20to%20media%20%E2%80%93%20the%20delegates%20loudly%20held%20forth%20on%20party%20policies%20and%20internal%20functioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20then%20and%20now%20is%20now.%20Consider%20last%20month%E2%80%99s%20National%20Council%20meeting.%20It%20was%20dominated%20by%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20address%20on%20both%20days%20and%20one%20each%20by%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20J.P.%20Nadda.%20The%2011-page%20%3Ca%20rel%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fopinion%2Fpolitically-correct%2Fswamy-impact-shifting-goalposts-7-takeaways-from-bjps-national-convention%2F1971311%2F%5C%22%3Epolitical%20resolution%3C%2Fa%3E%20mentioned%20Modi%20as%20many%20as%2084%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20the%20day%2C%20special%20trains%20carried%20party%20delegates%20who%20mingled%20with%20the%20large%20number%20of%20correspondents%20present.%20Top%20leaders%20like%20L.K.%20Advani%20and%20Murli%20Manohar%20Joshi%20accompanied%20the%20train%20and%20interacted%20with%20delegates%20and%20media%20persons%2C%20in%20groups%20and%20individually.%20We%20had%20a%20fairly%20good%20idea%20about%20what%20was%20happening%20in%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20presidents%2C%20on%20their%20part%2C%20did%20not%20announce%20any%20decision%20without%20consulting%20the%20NE%20or%20the%20office-bearers%20and%2C%20of%20course%2C%20the%20RSS.%20Nagpur%20in%20those%20days%20encouraged%20a%20system%20of%20free%20and%20fair%20internal%20debate%20among%20the%20Parivar%20outfits.%20The%20NE%20was%20a%20lively%20forum%20which%20discussed%20and%20worked%20for%20consensus%20on%20contentious%20issues%20%E2%80%93%20some%20thing%20unthinkable%20under%20the%20MoSha%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOften%20discussions%20were%20inconclusive%20and%20the%20NE%20had%20to%20put%20off%20consideration%20to%20the%20next%20meeting.%20For%20wider%20debate%20on%20specially%20contentious%20issues%2C%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98chintan%20baithaks%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20were%20called.%20Such%20a%20wider%20conclave%20was%20held%20at%20Sariska%20on%20Narasimha%20Rao%E2%80%99s%201991%20economic%20reform%20when%20the%20Advani%20group%20sharply%20differed%20with%20the%20Swadeshi%20Jagran%20Manch%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latter%20had%20the%20support%20of%20Murli%20Manohar%20Joshi%2C%20Malkani%2C%20K.L.%20Sharma%2C%20Sunder%20Singh%20Bhandari%20and%20Jai%20Dubashi.%20The%20Sariska%20conclave%20was%20followed%20by%20the%20Gandhinagar%20session%20of%20the%20NE%20where%20an%20economic%20policy%20document%20detailing%20the%20%E2%80%98Swadeshi%20alternative%E2%80%99%20or%20Gandhinagar%20declaration%20was%20finalised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOrganisational%20elections%20were%20fairly%20free.%20And%20at%20local%20levels%2C%20the%20pre-Modi%20BJP%20had%20its%20share%20of%20allegations%20of%20fake%20voters%20lists%2C%20protests%20and%20boycotts%20%E2%80%93%20indications%20of%20free%20and%20fair%20polls.%20Decisions%20under%20the%20central%20observers%20were%20mostly%20by%20consensus%20at%20tehsil%2C%20district%20and%20state%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20ministers%20were%20fixed%20after%20a%20system%20of%20tenuous%20consultations%20among%20the%20RSS%20leaders%2C%20BJP%20legislators%20and%20leaders%20of%20various%20contending%20state%20factions.%20Unlike%20today%2C%20the%20carried%20juicy%20stories%20about%20the%20prospects%20of%20different%20aspirants%20for%20the%20BJP%20CM%E2%80%99s%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20all%20this%20is%20history.%20The%20BJP%20as%20a%20political%20movement%20with%20organic%20links%20with%20its%20support%20base%20is%20a%20thing%20of%20past.%20Narendra%20Modi%20likes%20to%20directly%20deal%20with%20voters.%20Anything%20coming%20in%20between%20the%20leader%20and%20the%20voter%20is%20considered%20a%20hurdle%20and%20should%20be%20removed.%20That%20is%20the%20new%20philosophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20large%20army%20of%20middle-level%20workers%20who%20had%20acted%20as%20a%20link%20and%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20taking%20the%20message%20to%20the%20grassroots%20are%20another%20casualty.%20Under%20the%20Modi-centric%20public%20discourse%20and%20election%20campaign%2C%20they%20have%20little%20role.%20With%20technology%20and%20an%20army%20of%20experts%2C%20the%20whole%20line%20of%20command%20has%20undergone%20drastic%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20local%20levels%2C%20the%20traditional%20RSS%20and%20BJP%20workers%20have%20been%20turned%20into%20%3Cem%3Epanna%20pramukhs%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20booth%20in-charges%20and%20similar%20kind%20of%20gophers.%20All%20profitable%20positions%20have%20been%20cornered%20by%20the%20glib%20talking%20smart%20set.%20They%20invariably%20use%20their%20new%20status%20for%20the%20enhancement%20of%20their%20business%20career.%20With%20such%20elements%20grabbing%20the%20enormous%20party%20funds%2C%20devoted%20traditional%20workers%20are%20gradually%20fading%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20every%20good%20elected%20dictator%2C%20Modi%20has%20an%20aversion%20for%20leaders%20with%20their%20own%20support%20base.%20During%20the%20good%20old%20internal%20democracy%20days%2C%20such%20leaders%20were%20treated%20as%20a%20great%20asset%20to%20the%20BJP.%20But%20Modi%20considers%20them%20as%20irritants%20and%20potential%20challengers.%20Hence%20he%20has%20eliminated%20all%20senior%20chief%20ministers.%20Last%20among%20the%20sidelined%20are%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20Scindia%20and%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan.%20Their%20place%20has%20been%20taken%20by%20faceless%20new%20picks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Modi%20era%20also%20presents%20a%20curious%20paradox.%20While%20the%20Hindutva%20cause%20has%20floruised%20immensely%2C%20the%20RSS%20under%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%20has%20suffered%20considerable%20erosion.%20Modi%20increasingly%20overshadows%20Bhagwat%20and%20his%20RSS.%20Modi%20has%20taken%20the%20role%20of%20a%20chief%20priest%20and%20pujari%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20in%20Ayodhya%20or%20Abu%20Dhabi%20%E2%80%94%20and%20has%20been%20anointed%20as%20the%20Hindu%20Hriday%20Samrat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHindutva%20crowds%20increasingly%20look%20to%20Modi%20for%20inspiration%20and%20as%20their%20hero.%20The%20epicenter%20of%20Hindutva%20is%20gradually%20moving%20from%20Nagpur%20to%20the%20PMO%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20Modi%20has%20emerged%20as%20the%20chief%20spokesman%20of%20Hindutva.%20The%20RSS%20has%20never%20suffered%20such%20an%20erosion%20of%20authority%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reasons%20for%20this%20can%20be%20traced%20to%20the%20present%20RSS%20leadership%E2%80%99s%20tunnel%20vision.%20Bhagwat%E2%80%99s%20predecessors%20like%20Rajubhayya%20and%20K.S.%20Sudarshan%20had%20a%20wider%20world%20view%20beyond%20Hindutva%2C%20Ayodhya%20and%20narrow%20hate%20politics.%20They%20believed%20that%20Hindu%20nationalism%20could%20be%20built%20only%20by%20a%20BJP%20government%20on%20a%20nationalistic%20socio-economic%20foundation%2C%20i.e.%20a%20Swadeshi%20alternative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RSS%20never%20allowed%20the%20emergence%20of%20authoritarian%20or%20all-powerful%20super%20bosses%20under%20their%20aegis.%20Instead%2C%20they%20insisted%20on%20consensus%20decisions%20and%20collective%20leadership.%20Consider%20the%20travails%20of%20BJP%20Prime%20Minister%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20whenever%20he%20tried%20to%20cross%20the%20RSS%E2%80%99s%20Lakshman%20Rekha.%20Today%2C%20there%20is%20no%20line%20or%20limit%20Modi%20can%E2%80%99t%20cross.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EP.%20Raman%20is%20a%20veteran%20journalist%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710241755000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F12114331%2F33F81A3F-BCF6-4D05-975C-264958F029F4_1_105_c.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-rss-paradox-hindutva-is-gaining-fast-but-modi-is-stealing-rss-thunder%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20RSS%20never%20allowed%20the%20emergence%20of%20authoritarian%20super%20bosses%20under%20their%20aegis.%20Instead%2C%20they%20insisted%20on%20consensus%20decisions%20and%20collective%20leadership.%20Consider%20the%20travails%20of%20BJP%20Prime%20Minister%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20whenever%20he%20tried%20to%20cross%20the%20RSS%E2%80%99s%20Lakshman%20Rekha.%20Today%2C%20there%20is%20no%20line%20or%20limit%20Modi%20can%E2%80%99t%20cross.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-rss-paradox-hindutva-is-gaining-fast-but-modi-is-stealing-rss-thunder%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20unfollowed%20all%20momfluencers%20on%20social%20media.%20They%20were%20making%20me%20feel%20like%20a%20bad%20mom.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221687%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20posing%20for%20photo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e3a21090413ab8e1d8a46a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221265%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20unfollowed%20all%20momfluencers%20on%20social%20media.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI'm%20a%20mom%20of%20three%20kids%20and%20I've%20decided%20to%20unfollow%20momfluencers.%C