ntertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fwill-akshay-kumar-team-up-with-fukrey-director-mrigdeep-singh-lamba-for-a-comedy-film-heres-what-we-know%2Farticleshow%2F108435075.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20Is%20an%20Assault%20on%20Muslims%2C%20but%20It%20Will%20Come%20for%20Hindus%20Too%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12155110%2F640px-No_to_police_brutality_no_caa_no_nrc_graffiti_on_metro_wall_shaheen_bagh_protests_8_jan_2020.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20notification%20of%20the%20rules%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20came%20as%20no%20surprise%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Assam.%20They%20had%20been%20warned%20by%20their%20chief%20minister%2C%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%2C%20that%20the%20registration%20of%20political%20parties%20that%20dared%20to%20protest%20against%20CAA%20would%20be%20cancelled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Delhi%20too%2C%20activists%20living%20in%20predominantly%20%E2%80%98Muslim%20neighbourhoods%E2%80%99%20witnessed%20an%20unusually%20heavy%20deployment%20of%20security%20forces.%20Some%20of%20the%20activists%20were%20also%20contacted%20by%20the%20police%20and%20warned%20politely%20not%20to%20get%20involved%20in%20any%20agitational%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20interesting%20instead%20is%20the%20timing%20if%20its%20announcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20came%20right%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20dismissed%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20(SBI)%20plea%20to%20defer%20the%20date%20of%20revealing%20the%20details%20of%20the%20electoral%20bonds.%20It%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20major%20reversal%20and%20embarrassment%20for%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government.%20To%20prevent%20that%20from%20dominating%20the%20news%20space%2C%20another%20big%20news%20had%20to%20be%20manufactured.%20And%20what%20could%20be%20better%20than%20the%20notification%20of%20the%20CAA%20rules%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20of%20the%20CAA%20rules%20are%20yet%20another%20iteration%20of%20the%20ideology%20of%20the%20Modi%20government.%20It%20can%20be%20summarised%20in%20one%20sentence%3A%20to%20tell%20Muslims%20that%20they%20do%20not%20belong%20to%20India%20in%20the%20same%20measure%20or%20manner%20in%20which%20Hindus%20do.%20The%20state%20will%20find%20ways%20to%20accommodate%20Hindus%20and%20exclude%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20lawyer%20Aman%20Wadud%20has%20been%20saying%2C%20it%20is%20not%20going%20to%20help%20even%20the%20Hindus%20in%20Assam%2C%20who%20have%20been%20suffering%20after%20their%20exclusion%20from%20the%20NRC.%20It%E2%80%99s%20because%20they%20can%20not%20show%20the%20documents%20stipulated%20as%20essential%20to%20prove%20their%20belonging%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAA%20claims%20to%20be%20an%20instrument%20that%20will%20help%20people%20of%20all%20religions%2C%20barring%20Muslims%2C%20who%20have%20suffered%20persecution%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20Afghanistan%20and%20Bangladesh.%20But%20it%20brings%20no%20relief%20to%20those%20Hindus%20who%20have%20declared%20that%20they%20are%20citizens%20of%20India%20but%20cannot%20show%20the%20papers%20asked%20by%20the%20BJP%20government%20to%20prove%20their%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20government%20and%20its%20leaders%20have%20been%20saying%20that%20all%20Hindus%20would%20be%20included%20under%20the%20purview%20of%20the%20act.%20But%20how%3F%20The%20CAA%20asks%20them%20to%20show%20that%20they%20were%20citizens%20of%20Pakistan%2C%20Bangladesh%20or%20Afghanistan.%20How%20will%20they%20do%20it%3F%20These%20Hindu%20citizens%2C%20numbering%20approximately%2015%20lakhs%2C%20would%20be%20left%20stateless.%20We%20must%20understand%20this%20before%20going%20into%20the%20real%20intent%20of%20the%20CAA%20and%20how%20it%20affects%20the%20secular%20character%20of%20Indian%20citizenship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20notification%20of%20CAA%2C%20the%20grounds%20of%20Indian%20citizenship%20have%20officially%20opened%20a%20path%20towards%20%E2%80%9Cfaith-based%E2%80%9D%20citizenship%20%E2%80%93%20a%20path%20open%20to%20everyone%20but%20Muslims.%20The%20real%20intent%20and%20impact%20of%20the%20CAA%20cannot%20be%20understood%20if%20we%20do%20not%20read%20it%20along%20with%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20(NRC).%20After%20all%2C%20the%20home%20minister%20has%20been%20very%20clear%20about%20one%20gaining%20meaning%20in%20the%20company%20of%20the%20other.%20NRC%20is%20a%20process%20of%20exclusion%20and%20CAA%2C%20one%20of%20inclusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20leaders%2C%20including%20the%20home%20minister%2C%20have%20said%20time%20and%20again%20that%20NRC%20would%20weed%20out%20outsiders%20while%20CAA%20would%20include%20the%20left%20out%20Hindus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20needs%20to%20be%20underlined%20that%20NRC%20brings%20a%20very%20significant%20change%20in%20the%20concept%20of%20Indian%20citizenship.%20With%20the%20NRC%2C%20we%20already%20saw%20a%20shift%20from%3Cem%3E%20jus%20soli%3C%2Fem%3E%20(citizenship%20by%20birth)%20to%20%3Cem%3Ejus%20sanguinis%3C%2Fem%3E%20(citizenship%20by%20descent).%20However%2C%20the%20affinity%20of%20CAA%20with%20NRC%20is%20not%20only%20fundamental%20but%20critical%20to%20its%20implementation%20in%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20CAA-NRC%20really%20excluding%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssam%20was%20made%20the%20perfect%20laboratory%20to%20execute%20this%20model%20of%20citizenship%20re-verification%20through%20NRC.%20Of%20course%2C%20the%20state%20provided%20organic%20grounds%20to%20implement%20something%20like%20this%20due%20to%20the%20existing%20demands%20of%20the%20Assamese%20nationalists.%20The%20use%20of%20NRC%20to%20identify%20%E2%80%98foreigners%E2%80%99%20in%20Assam%20meant%20anyone%20who%20had%20ancestry%20in%20erstwhile%20East%20Bengal%2C%20Hindu%20or%20Muslim.%20Their%20religion%20didn%E2%80%99t%20matter%20to%20the%20Assamese%20nationalist%20whose%20long-standing%20demand%20was%20to%20identify%20those%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20Bengali%E2%80%9D%20migrants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENRC%20left%20out%20over%2019%20lakh%20people%20from%20the%20citizenship%20register.%20According%20to%20a%20Sabrang%20report%2C%20sourced%20to%20the%20Intelligence%20Brunch%20of%20Assam%2C%20only%20about%204.89%20lakh%20of%20the%20total%20belonged%20to%20Bengali%20origin%20Muslim%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERest%20of%20the%20breakup%20is%20as%20follows%3A%20Bengali%20Hindus%20(6.90%20lakhs)%2C%20Gorkha%20(85%2C000)%2C%20Assamese%20Hindu%20(60%2C000)%2C%20Koch%20Rajbonshi%20(58%2C000)%2C%20Goria%20Moria%20Deshi%20(35%2C000)%2C%20Bodo%20(20%2C000)%2C%20Karbi%20(9%2C000)%2C%20Rabha%20(8%2C000)%2C%20Hajong%20(8%2C000)%2C%20Mishing%20(7%2C000)%2C%20Ahom%20(3%2C000)%2C%20Garo%20(2%2C500)%2C%20Matak%20(1%2C500)%2C%20Dimasa%20(1%2C100)%2C%20Sonowal%20Kachari%20(1%2C000)%2C%20Maran%20(900)%2C%20Bishnupriya%20Manipuri%20(200)%2C%20Naga%20(125)%2C%20Hmar%20(75)%2C%20Kuki%20(85)%2C%20Thadou%20(50)%2C%20Baite%20(85).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20one%20can%20see%2C%20only%20a%20few%20of%20these%20people%20qualify%20to%20apply%20for%20citizenship%20under%20CAA.%20Technically%2C%20the%20category%20of%20Original%20Inhabitants%20(OI)%20also%20takes%20away%20the%20doubt%20of%20many%20communities%20listed%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20notification%20of%20CAA%2C%20the%20only%20community%20left%20out%20are%20the%20Bengali%20origin%20Muslim%20community%20in%20Assam.%20This%20makes%20them%20the%20primary%20political%20victims%20of%20the%20citizenship%20process%20of%20NRC.%20One%20can%20safely%20conclude%20that%20both%20the%20process%20are%20anti-Muslim%20projects%20of%20the%20Indian%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Saviour%20complex%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notification%20also%20comes%20with%20a%20tone%20of%20saviour%20complex.%20It%20is%20trying%20to%20claim%20that%20India%2C%20through%20CAA%2C%20is%20going%20to%20save%20the%20non-Muslim%20persecuted%20minorities%20in%20its%20neighbouring%20countries.%20Such%20is%20the%20control%20of%20the%20narrative%20in%20India.%20But%20we%20need%20to%20ask%20again%2C%20what%20about%20those%20poor%20Hindus%20who%20could%20not%20show%20the%20papers%3F%20The%20CAA%20don%E2%80%99t%20help%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20can%20say%2C%20and%20rightly%20so%2C%20that%20the%20objective%20of%20the%20announcement%20was%20never%20to%20help%20any%20community%20but%20to%20create%20an%20atmosphere%20in%20which%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20are%20placed%20on%20unequal%20planes.%20As%20Sushil%20Aaron%20wrote%20way%20back%20in%202019%2C%20%E2%80%9CRegardless%20of%20which%20process%20is%20applied%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20the%20NRC%20process%20has%20been%20conceived%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20spares%20Hindus%2C%20for%20the%20most%20part%2C%20the%20trouble%20of%20proving%20they%20are%20Indian%20citizens%2C%20since%20the%20CAA%20eventually%20offers%20pathways%20to%20Indian%20citizenship%20for%20them%20in%20a%20way%20that%20it%20does%20not%20provide%20to%20Muslims.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20of%20the%20CAA%20rules%20is%20a%20psychological%20assault%20on%20Muslims%20by%20reinforcing%20anxieties%20about%20their%20existence%20as%20equal%20citizens.%20One%20CAA%20is%20here%2C%20can%20NRC%20be%20far%20behind%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notification%20of%20CAA%20also%20comes%20during%20the%20holy%20month%20of%20Ramadan.%20The%20timing%20of%20this%20declaration%20is%20a%20symbolic%20gesture%20that%20is%20pregnant%20with%20violence%20against%20a%20community.%20This%20violence%20is%2C%20above%20all%20symbolic%2C%20in%20nature.%20In%20a%20month%20when%20peace%2C%20generosity%20and%20justice%2C%20among%20other%20things%2C%20is%20celebrated%20as%20virtues%2C%20this%20declaration%20is%20a%20stab%20at%20the%20very%20secularity%20of%20citizenship%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EApoorvanand%20is%20a%20professor%20at%20Delhi%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESuraj%20Gogoi%20writes%20about%20citizenship%2C%20minority%2C%20nationalism%2C%20state%2C%20food%20and%20violence%20in%20South%20Asia.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710241221000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12155110%2F640px-No_to_police_brutality_no_caa_no_nrc_graffiti_on_metro_wall_shaheen_bagh_protests_8_jan_2020.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fcitizenship-amendment-act-is-an-assault-on-muslims-but-it-will-come-for-hindus-too%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20act%2C%20while%20eviscerating%20the%20secular%20fabric%20of%20the%20country%2C%20also%20offers%20no%20relief%20to%20those%20Hindus%20who%20have%20declared%20that%20they%20are%20citizens%20of%20India%20but%20cannot%20show%20the%20papers%20asked%20by%20the%20BJP%20government%20to%20prove%20their%20claim.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fcitizenship-amendment-act-is-an-assault-on-muslims-but-it-will-come-for-hindus-too%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Finnish%20Comedy%20About%20Feminist%20Porn%20%E2%80%98Money%20Shot%E2%80%99%20Heads%20to%20Canneseries%3A%20%E2%80%98It%E2%80%99s%20Definitely%20Not%20Another%20Nordic%20Noir!%E2%80%99%20(EXCLUSIVE)%26nbsp%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710241111000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FMoney-Shot.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D562%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235939233%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Finnish%20comedy%20%E2%80%9CMoney%20Shot%2C%E2%80%9D%20about%20an%20ex-porn%20star%20venturing%20out%20of%20her%20comfort%20zone%2C%20is%20he