006285%5C%22%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Virat%20was%20informed%20by%20Agarkar%20about%20the%20need%20for%20a%20change%20in%20his%20approach.%20The%20conversation%20prompted%20Kohli%20to%20bat%20more%20aggressively%20in%20T20Is%20against%20Afghanistan%20but%20could%20only%20register%20the%20highest%20score%20of%2029%20in%20a%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20further%20claims%20that%20the%20selectors%20are%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%20the%20slow%20wickets%20in%20the%20West%20Indies%20wouldn't%20suit%20Kohli's%20natural%20game%20as%20a%20batter.%20Hence%2C%20the%20selection%20committee%20has%20been%20assessing%20its%20options%20for%20the%20showpiece%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20selector%2C%20Agarkar%2C%20has%20also%20reportedly%20taken%20up%20the%20task%20to%20convince%20Kohli%20that%20he%20has%20to%20make%20way%20for%20the%20younger%20generation%20in%20the%20shortest%20format.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20likes%20of%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%2C%20Rinku%20Singh%2C%20Tilak%20Varma%2C%20and%20Shivam%20Dube%20are%20some%20of%20the%20players%20who%20could%20be%20used%20in%20the%20middle-order%20if%20Kohli%20steps%20aside.%20But%2C%20all%20is%20not%20over%20for%20Kohli%20yet.%20It%20is%20also%20believed%20that%20Virat's%20fortunes%20could%20change%20if%20he%20goes%20on%20to%20have%20an%20exemplary%20season%20with%20the%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bangalore%2C%20prove%20the%20selectors%20that%20he%20can%20play%20in%20the%20modern%20T20%20mould.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Kohli%20hasn't%20yet%20joined%20the%20RCB%20camp%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%20IPL%202024%20season.%20He%20gave%20the%20entire%20England%20Test%20series%20a%20miss%20because%20of%20the%20birth%20of%20his%20son%20Akaay.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710241080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fq247ogog_virat-kohli-bcci_625x300_07_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fconvince-virat-kohli-to-make-way-for-youngsters-