.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fjeh-ali-khan-and-kareena-kapoor-khan-set-the-fashion-mood-right-like-always-in-the-latest-click%2Farticleshow%2F108434840.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20Camera%2C%20Pilot%20Ejects%20From%20Crashing%20Tejas%2C%20Parachutes%20To%20Safety%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Tejas%20fighter%20jet%2C%20India's%20indigenous%20fighter%20jet%2C%20crashed%20today%20in%20Rajasthan's%20Jaisalmer%20near%20a%20hostel%20complex.%20The%20pilot%20ejected%20safely%20from%20the%20aircraft%20but%20the%20jet%20was%20up%20in%20flames.%20The%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20has%20ordered%20a%20court%20of%20inquiry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20of%20the%20pilot%20ejecting%20from%20the%20jet%20showed%20the%20fighter%20jet%20gliding%20at%20a%20low%20altitude.%20The%20jet%20glides%20right%20to%20left%20in%20the%20camera%20frame%20and%20the%20pilot%20opens%20the%20parachute%20and%20descends%20toward%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tejas%2C%20which%20is%20not%20manned%2C%20is%20losing%20altitude%20and%20crashed%20on%20the%20ground%20of%20the%20student's%20hostel%20several%20metres%20away.%20A%20white%20parachute%20is%20seen%20coming%20down.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pilots%20pull%20the%20ejection%20seat%20and%20explosives%20under%20the%20seat%20blow%20the%20canopy%20of%20the%20fighter%20jet%20and%20throw%20the%20pilot%20up%20in%20the%20air.%20The%20rockets%20under%20the%20seat%20direct%20the%20pilot%20in%20a%20safe%20direction%20and%20parachutes%20are%20deployed.%20During%20ejection%2C%20the%20pilots%20experience%20high%20g-forces%20reaching%20up%20to%2020%20times%20the%20force%20experienced%20on%20earth%2C%20which%20can%20cause%20severe%20injuries%20and%20can%20even%20bar%20them%20from%20flying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EZero-Zero%20Ejection%20Seat%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEjection%20seats%20lift%20the%20pilot%20out%20of%20the%20aircraft%20to%20a%20safe%20distance%2C%20then%20deploy%20a%20parachute%20to%20allow%20the%20pilot%20to%20land%20safely%20on%20the%20ground.%20Tejas%20uses%20the%20British-manufactured%2C%20Martin%20Baker%2C%20zero-zero%20ejection%20seats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20zero-zero%20ejection%20seats%20are%20designed%20to%20eject%20pilots%20from%20zero%20position%20i.e.%20stationary%20position%20at%20a%20considerable%20height%20to%20deploy%20parachutes.%20Zero%20position%20refers%20to%20zero%20altitude%20or%20zero%20speed.%20In%20the%20video%20of%20the%20crash%2C%20the%20pilot%20can%20be%20seen%20ejecting%20safely%20from%20several%20feet%20above%20the%20ground.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20zero-zero%20capability%20was%20developed%20to%20help%20pilots%20escape%20from%20unrecoverable%20situations%20during%20low-altitude%20or%20low-speed%20flights%20as%20well%20as%20ground%20mishaps%20during%20takeoff%20or%20landing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ejection%20seat%20is%20part%20of%20the%20overall%20'Egress'%20system%2C%20which%20means%20the%20%26quot%3Bway%20to%20exit%26quot%3B.%20The%20system%20includes%20explosives%20under%20the%20seat%2C%20the%20canopy%2C%20and%20parachutes.%20The%20angle%20of%20ejection%20is%20crucial.%20The%20fighter%20jet%20moves%20forward%20and%20the%20line%20of%20ejection%20is%20perpendicular%20to%20it%20to%20move%20the%20pilot%20away%20from%20the%20aircraft.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Tejas%20Programme%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20twin-seater%20fighter%20jet%2C%20the%20co-pilot%20ejects%20first%20and%20then%20the%20lead%20pilot%20who%20sits%20in%20front.%20The%20temperature%20of%20the%20air%20blast%20during%20ejection%20is%20very%20high%20and%20if%20the%20lead%20pilot%20ejects%20first%2C%20then%20the%20co-pilot%20may%20suffer%20serious%20burn%20injuries.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETejas%20is%20a%20sin