80%A6%3Cbr%3E%5CnWe%20said%20that%20we%20would%20bring%20the%20CAA...%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FQAlQ2UMQ8S%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FQAlQ2UMQ8S%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Amit%20Shah%20(Modi%20Ka%20Parivar)%20(%40AmitShah)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAmitShah%2Fstatus%2F1767487767041204650%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2012%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Home%20Minister%20said%20crores%20of%20people%20fled%20to%20India%20from%20Pakistan%20and%20Bangladesh%20to%20%26quot%3Bsave%20their%20religion%20and%20honour%26quot%3B%2C%20but%20did%20not%20get%20citizenship.%20%26quot%3BWithout%20citizenship%2C%20they%20would%20suffer%20insults%20in%20their%20own%20country.%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20honoured%20Hindus%2C%20Buddhists%2C%20Jains%20and%20Sikhs%20by%20granting%20them%20citizenship%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20said%20the%20BJP-led%20central%20government%20has%20worked%20to%20ensure%20a%20dignified%20life%20for%20these%20refugees.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20acted%20to%20protect%20their%20culture%2C%20language%2C%20their%20religion%20and%20the%20honour%20of%20the%20women%20in%20their%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BFrom%20now%20on%2C%20every%20refugee%20in%20this%20country%20has%20the%20same%20right%20as%20you%20or%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Home%20Minister's%20sharp%20counter-attack%20comes%20amid%20an%20Opposition%20charge%20over%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20citizenship%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20Opposition%20Congress%20has%20questioned%20the%20timing%20of%20CAA's%20implementation%2C%20accusing%20the%20BJP%20of%20trying%20to%20polarise%20voters%20ahead%20of%20elections.%20Party%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20has%20termed%20it%20%26quot%3BBJP's%20desperate%20attempt%20at%20divisive%20politics%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20Congress%20chief%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20warned%20people%20against%20applying%20for%20citizenship%20under%20the%20new%20law.%20%26quot%3BBJP%20leaders%20say%20CAA%20gives%20you%20rights.%20But%20the%20moment%20you%20apply%20for%20citizenship%2C%20you%20become%20illegal%20migrants%20and%20you%20will%20lose%20your%20rights.%20You%20will%20lose%20rights%20and%20be%20taken%20to%20detention%20camps.%20Please%20think%20before%20you%20apply%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20has%20said.%20%26quot%3BHave%20you%20ever%20heard%20of%20citizenship%20based%20on%20religion%3F%20This%20is%20an%20insult%20of%20humanity%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20has%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDMK%20president%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20has%20said%20CAA%20is%20%26quot%3Bdivisive%26quot%3B%20and%20against%20India's%20pluralism%20and%20secularism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20new%20law%2C%20non-Muslim%20migrants%20from%20Bangladesh%2C%20Pakistan%20and%20Afghanistan%20fleeing%20religious%20persecution%20can%20seek%20Indian%20citizenship.%20Persons%20from%20Hindu%2C%20Sikh%2C%20Buddhist%2C%20Jain%2C%20Parsi%20or%20Christian%20communities%20from%20these%20countries%2C%20who%20entered%20India%20on%20or%20before%20December%2031%2C%202014%2C%20can%20seek%20citizenship%20under%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710240540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fbifd0t58_amit-shah-ani_625x300_12_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcaa-amit-shah-amit-shahs-counter-strike-amid-opposition-protests-over-citizenship-law-5224394%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Countering%20the%20Opposition's%20charge%20over%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20today%20said%20the%20Congress%20had%20opposed%20the%20law%20for%20%26quot%3Bappeasement%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bvote%20bank%20politics%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-n