Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fk-pop%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fbts-jimin-finds-himself-linked-to-ryan-goslings-iconic-oscar-performance-heres-why%2Farticleshow%2F108434447.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108434447.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20curious%20connection%20between%20Jimin%20and%20Gosling's%20performance%20stems%20from%20an%20earlier%20revelation%20when%20clips%20of%20the%20movie%20surfaced%2C%20showcasing%20Gosling%20adorned%20in%20outfit%20similar%20to%20the%20BTS%20member's%20iconic%20look%20from%20the%20%E2%80%98Permission%20To%20Dance%E2%80%99%20music%20video.%20The%20resemblance%20in%20their%20attire%20sparked%20a%20playful%20exchange%20between%20the%20two%20stars%2C%20with%20Gosling%20extending%20a%20special%20message%20to%20Jimin%20through%20social%20media%2C%20accompanied%20by%20a%20promise%20of%20a%20unique%20gift%20%E2%80%93%20his%20guitar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fk-pop%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fbts-jimin-finds-himself-linked-to-ryan-goslings-iconic-oscar-performance-heres-why%2Farticleshow%2F108434447.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meet%20The%20Woman%20Scientist%20Behind%20Agni-5%20Missile%20With%20Multiple%20Warheads%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20successfully%20tested%20the%20Agni-5%20missile%20with%20multiple%20warheads%20yesterday%20and%20the%20massive%20feat%20was%20announced%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20who%20called%20it%20'Mission%20Divyastra'.%20The%20project%20was%20led%20by%20a%20woman%20scientist%20from%20the%20country's%20missile%20complex%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20Sheena%20Rani%2C%20who%20has%20been%20working%20on%20the%20Agni%20missile%20systems%20since%201999.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Agni-5%20missile%20with%20Multiple%20Independently%20Targetable%20Re-entry%20Vehicle%20(MIRV)%20technology%20is%20being%20termed%20by%20many%20as%20the%20crowning%20glory%20for%20her%20twenty-fifth%20year%20at%20India's%20defence%20research%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20a%20proud%20member%20of%20the%20DRDO%20fraternity%20that%20helps%20protect%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20asserts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20follows%20in%20the%20illustrious%20footsteps%20of%20India's%20legendary%20missile%20technologist%20'Agni%20Putri'%20Tessy%20Thomas%2C%20who%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20the%20development%20of%20the%20Agni%20series%20of%20missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnown%20as%20a%20'powerhouse%20of%20energy'%2C%20the%2057-year-old%20is%20a%20scientist%20at%20the%20Advanced%20Systems%20Laboratory%20of%20the%20Defence%20Research%20Development%20Organisation%20(DRDO)%20in%20Hyderabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20trained%20electronics%20and%20communications%20engineer%20with%20expertise%20in%20computer%20science%20Sheena%20Rani%20studied%20at%20the%20College%20of%20Engineering%20in%20Thiruvananthapuram.%20She%20worked%20for%20eight%20years%20at%20India's%20foremost%20civilian%20rocketry%20lab%2C%20the%20Vikram%20Sarabhai%20Space%20Center%20(VSSC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPost%20the%20Pokhran%20Nuclear%20test%20of%201998%2C%20she%20moved%20to%20the%20DRDO%20as%20a%20lateral%20entry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%201999%2C%20Ms%20Rani%20has%20been%20working%20on%20the%20launch%20control%20systems%20for%20the%20entire%20Agni%20series%20of%20missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20draws%20inspiration%20and%20motivation%20from%20India's%20'Missile%20Man'%20former%20President%20of%20India%20and%20former%20head%20of%20the%20DRDO%2C%20Dr%20APJ%20Abdul%20Kalam.%20Interestingly%2C%20she%20mirrors%20Dr%20Kalam's%20career%20path%2C%20since%20he%20also%20started%20his%20career%20at%20the%20ISRO's%20Vikram%20Sarabhai%20Space%20Center%20and%20then%20moved%20to%20the%20DRDO%20to%20lead%20the%20Integrated%20Guided%20Missile%20Development%20Program.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20person%20who%20has%20helped%20her%20shape%20her%20career%2C%20she%20says%2C%20is%20Dr%20Avinash%20Chander%2C%20the%20missile%20technologist%20who%20led%20DRDO%20through%20some%20difficult%20years.%20Dr%20Chander%20described%20Sheena%20Rani%20as%20%26quot%3Balways%20smiling%2C%20willing%20to%20innovate%20and%20her%20dedication%20to%20the%20Agni%20missile%20program%20is%20spectacular%2C%20yesterday's%20launch%20was%20a%20crowning%20glory%20for%20her%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20husband%2C%20PSRS%20Sastry%2C%20also%20worked%20with%20the%20DRDO%20on%20missiles%20and%20was%20also%20in-charge%20of%20the%20Kautilya%20Satellite%20launched%20by%20ISRO%20in%202019%20and%20used%20for%20gathering%20electronic%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DRDO%20confirmed%20it%20conducted%20the%20first%20successful%20flight%20test%20of%20the%20indigenously%20developed%20Agni-5%20missile%20with%20Multiple%20Independently%20Targetable%20Re-Entry%20Vehicle%20(%20MIRV)%20technology.%20The%20flight%20test%20named%20'Mission%20Divyastra'%20was%20carried%20out%20from%20Dr%20APJ%20Abdul%20Kalam%20Island%20in%20Odisha.%20Various%20Telemetry%20and%20radar%20stations%20tracked%20and%20monitored%20multiple%20re-entry%20vehicles.%20The%20mission%20accomplished%20the%20designed%20parameters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Shri%20Narendra%20Modi%20praised%20the%20efforts%20of%20the%20DRDO%20scientists%20who%20participated%20in%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20complex%20Mission.%20In%20a%20post%20on%20social%20media%20platform%20X%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BProud%20of%20our%20DRDO%20scientists%20for%20Mission%20Divyastra%2C%20the%20first%20flight%20test%20of%20indigenously%20developed%20Agni-5%20missile%20with%20Multiple%20Independently%20Targetable%20Re-entry%20Vehicle%20(MIRV)%20technology.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20missile%20is%20a%20game%20changer%20for%20regional%20geopolitics%20and%20a%20force%20multiplier%20and%20made%20with%20state-of-the-art%2C%20complex%20indigenous%20technology.%20The%20team%20is%20right%20now%20full%20of%20pride%20after%20having%20met%20all%20the%20intended%20objectives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20weapon%20system%20made%20by%20the%20DRDO%20has%20MIRV%20technology%2C%20which%20ensures%20that%20a%20single%20missile%20can%20deploy%20multiple%20war%20heads%20and%20hit%20targets%20at%20different%20locations%20simultaneously.%20It%20can%20help%20evade%20enemy%20anti-ballistic%20missile%20system%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%2C%20India%20has%20joined%20the%20select%20club%20of%20nations%20-%20US%2C%20UK%2C%20Russia%2C%20France%20and%20China%20-%20that%20have%20the%20MIRV%20technology.%20India%20is%20the%20sixth%20country%20to%20have%20MIRV-capable%20missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20MIRV%20payload%20involves%20a%20single%20missile%20carrying%20several%20nuclear%20warheads%2C%20each%20programmed%20to%20hit%20a%20separate%20target.%20This%20means%20the%20optimum%20use%20of%20a%20single%20missile%20and%20gives%20India%20the%20capability%20of%20targeting%20adversaries%20in%20the%20east%20and%20west%20within%20a%205%2C000-plus%20km%20radius.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20this%20effective%2C%20the%20system%20is%20also%20equipped%20with%20indigenous%20avionics%20systems%20and%20high-accuracy%20sensor%20packages%2C%20which%20ensure%20that%20the%20re-entry%20vehicles%20accurately%20reach%20the%20target%20points%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710240060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fc9a086bs_sheena-rani_625x300_12_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmission-divyastra-meet-the-woman-scientist-sheena-rani-behind-agni-5-missile-with-multiple-warheads-5224381%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20successfully%20tested%20the%20Agni-5%20missile%20with%20multiple%20warheads%20yesterday%20and%20the%20massive%20feat%20was%20announced%2