n%20so%20strongly%20rebuked%20by%20a%20Court.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20responded%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Monday%2C%20Justice%20Lokur%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9Cat%20every%20stage%20there%20were%20problems%20that%20the%20SBI%20was%20trying%20to%20create.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%2025-minute%20interview%20to%20Karan%20Thapar%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Justice%20Lokur%20was%20asked%20if%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20handling%20of%20the%20electoral%20bond%20issue%2C%20both%20in%20February%20and%20yesterday%20(Monday%2011)%2C%20indicates%20a%20new%20assertiveness%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20Court%20and%20a%20new%20firmness%20in%20defence%20of%20the%20rights%20of%20Indian%20citizens%2C%20and%20Justice%20Lokur%20replied%3A%20%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20I%20hope%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20sign%20of%20assertiveness%E2%80%9D%20adding%20that%20he%20would%20welcome%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FsFFkcewRp18%3Fsi%3D2QzttntB5RMllnMm%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERight%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20interview%20there%20is%20also%20a%20five-minute%20discussion%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20light%20of%20Justice%20Lokur%E2%80%99s%20hope%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20now%20more%20assertive%20%E2%80%93%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20whether%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20should%20stay%20the%20Act%20passed%20in%20December%20determining%20how%20Election%20Commissioners%20and%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioners%20are%20appointed.%20This%20Act%20has%20been%20challenged%20in%20Court%20and%20the%20Court%20has%20agreed%20to%20hear%20the%20challenge%20but%20as%20yet%20no%20date%20for%20t