20from%20them.%20The%20event%20ended%20with%20the%20host%20reminding%20the%20audience%20that%20even%20those%20present%20in%20the%20room%20were%20part%20of%20the%20ongoing%20resistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Jawahar%20Bhawan%20event%2C%20residents%20of%20Shiv%20Vihar%2C%20Mustafabad%2C%20Jaffrabad%2C%20and%20other%20locations%20in%20Northeast%20Delhi%20narrated%20with%20great%20strength%20and%20kindness%20the%20impact%20that%20resistance%20had%20on%20them%20%E2%80%93%20how%20important%20Justice%20Muralidhar%E2%80%99s%20midnight%20order%20was%20in%20reducing%20violence%20in%20the%20Hindutva-led%20riots%2C%20what%20it%20meant%20that%20we%20were%20gathered%20there%20to%20understand%20the%20growth%20of%20hate%20crime%20in%20India%2C%20and%20how%20the%20efforts%20of%20lawyers%2C%20filmmakers%2C%20poets%2C%20doctors%2C%20and%20activists%20were%20essential%20in%20continuing%20to%20care%20for%20justice.%20I%20felt%20hope%20despite%20the%20worries%20that%20any%20amount%20of%20visibility%2C%20even%20in%20the%20most%20tender%20efforts%20to%20provide%20care%20for%20those%20who%20had%20lost%20loved%20ones%2C%20homes%2C%20and%20livelihoods%2C%20would%20mean%20a%20possibility%20of%20state-enabled%20persecution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Jawahar%20Bhawan%20event%2C%20residents%20of%20Shiv%20Vihar%2C%20Mustafabad%2C%20Jaffrabad%2C%20and%20other%20locations%20in%20Northeast%20Delhi%20shared%20their%20stories%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20resistance.%20They%20spoke%20about%20the%20significance%20of%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fdont-know-why-delhi-riots-order-upset-the-government-it-was-the-right-thing-to-do-justice-muralidhar-239588%5C%22%3E%20Justice%20Muralidhar%E2%80%99s%20midnight%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20quelling%20violence%20during%20the%20riots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20saw%20discussions%20on%20the%20rise%20of%20hate%20crimes%20in%20India%20and%20highlighted%20the%20indispensable%20role%20of%20lawyers%2C%20filmmakers%2C%20poets%2C%20doctors%2C%20and%20activists%20in%20pursuing%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20concerns%20about%20potential%20state-enabled%20persecution%2C%20there%20was%20a%20palpable%20sense%20of%20hope%20fueled%20by%20the%20collective%20efforts%20to%20provide%20care%20and%20support%20to%20those%20who%20had%20lost%20loved%20ones%2C%20homes%2C%20and%20livelihoods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2011%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fcentre-implements-citizenship-amendment-act-check-the-caa-rules-here-92081%5C%22%3Ethe%20Centre%20notified%20the%20Rules%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%20(CAA)%20after%20four%20years%20of%20continuously%20filing%20extensions.%20The%20move%20came%20a%20few%20hours%20after%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Felectoral-bonds-sbi-just-has-to-open-sealed-cover-give-details-sc-raps-bank-101710136137207.html%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%20rapped%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20their%20lack%20of%20compliance%20with%20releasing%20data%20on%20electoral%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20soon%20as%20the%20news%20arrived%2C%20chatter%20began%20on%20the%20move%E2%80%99s%20form%2C%20intent%2C%20and%20motive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20sense%20of%20anxiety%20overwhelmed%20me%2C%20of%20what%20this%20meant%20and%20what%20now%20needed%20to%20be%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20ministers%20of%20the%20governments%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fmatuas-welcome-caa-rules-mamata-threatens-opposition-if-rules-are-discriminatory%2Farticle67940159.ece%5C%22%3EWest%20Bengal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Fnotification-of-caa-rules-pm-modis-attempt-to-salvage-his-sinking-ship-cm-stalin%2F1996976%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%2520a%2520social%2520media%2520post%2Cdivision%25E2%2580%259D%252C%2520he%2520further%2520said.%5C%22%3ETamil%20Nadu%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fcaa-an-open-challenge-to-humanity-kerala-will-not-implement-it-cm-pinarayi-vijayan-101710168562847.html%5C%22%3EKerala%3C%2Fa%3E%20released%20statements%2C%20expressing%20their%20condemnation%20of%20the%20CAA%2C%20and%20the%20continued%20insistence%20that%20the%20discriminatory%20Act%20would%20not%20be%20implemented%20in%20their%20states%20and%20would%20be%20fought.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20decried%20it%20as%20a%20deliberate%20move%20of%20electoral%20politics%2C%20questioning%20why%20the%20Centre%20released%20the%20Rules%20at%20this%20moment%20after%20four%20years%20of%20delays%2C%20and%20condemning%20the%20exclusion%20of%20Muslims%2C%20Sri%20Lankan%20Tamils%2C%20and%20many%20others%20from%20the%20Rules%E2%80%99%20criteria.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scholar%20Angshuman%20Choudhury%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fangshuman_ch%2Fstatus%2F1767190089560408199%5C%22%3Easked%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehow%20exactly%20the%20government%20would%20verify%20claims%20of%20religious%20persecution%2C%20what%20parameters%20would%20be%20used%2C%20and%20what%20digital%20security%20measures%20were%20in%20place%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20personal%20data%20of%20applicants%20would%20remain%20safe.%20He%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fangshuman_ch%2Fstatus%2F1767237983760224440%5C%22%3Ewrote%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20the%20legal%20details%20of%20the%20Rules%20don%E2%80%99t%20matter%20as%20much%20as%20the%20Act%20being%20used%20as%20a%20tool%20for%20right-wing%20groups%20to%20further%20%E2%80%9Cbully%20Indian%20Muslims%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsaduddin%20Owaisi%20further%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fasadowaisi%2Fstatus%2F1767182248246178025%5C%22%3Econnected%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethe%20announcement%20of%20the%20Rules%20as%20being%20linked%20to%20the%20election%20period%20and%20criticised%20the%20CAA%20for%20its%20divisive%20nature%2C%20as%20based%20on%20Nathuram%20Godse%E2%80%99s