t%20the%20flood%20was%20that%20it%20wasn't%20from%20my%20pipes%3B%20it%20started%20from%20the%20neighbor%20two%20floors%20up%20and%20eventually%20ended%20in%20my%20condo%20(on%20the%20first%20floor).%20The%20damage%20was%20extensive.%20An%20inch%20of%20water%20covered%20my%20entire%20place.%20My%20relaxing%20holiday%20was%20cut%20short%2C%20and%20the%20following%20months%20were%20nothing%20like%20I'd%20ever%20experienced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20had%20my%20share%20of%20car%20accidents%20and%20auto%20insurance%20claims%2C%20but%20this%20was%20my%20first%20time%20having%20a%20major%20loss%20and%20filing%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-renters-insurance-companies%5C%22%3Erenters%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E%20claim.%20Here%20are%20the%20most%20valuable%20lessons%20I%20learned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E1.%20Make%20sure%20you%20have%20enough%20coverage%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20was%20time%20to%20get%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-is-renters-insurance%5C%22%3Erenters%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20did%20what%20most%20people%20do%20when%20valuing%20my%20personal%20property%3A%20make%20a%20wild%20guess%20and%20hope%20for%20the%20best.%20I%20had%20never%20reviewed%20my%20belongings%20in%20detail%20to%20see%20if%20my%20coverage%20limit%20was%20sufficient%2C%20even%20after%20inheriting%20antique%20furniture%20and%20purchasing%20high-quality%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20filing%20my%20claim%20with%20the%20insurance%20company%2C%20I%20had%20to%20make%20a%20list%20of%20everything%20that%20needed%20to%20be%20replaced%2C%20including%20the%20approximate%20value%20of%20each%20item.%20Seeing%20the%20amounts%20add%20up%20made%20me%20realize%20that%20I%20was%20significantly%20underinsured.%20I%20lost%20about%20half%20of%20my%20possessions%2C%20valued%20at%20nearly%20my%20full%20coverage%20amount.%20I%20would%20have%20been%20on%20the%20hook%20for%20thousands%20more%20if%20I%20had%20experienced%20a%20total%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20my%20claim%20was%20finalized%20and%20I%20started%20replacing%20items%2C%20I%20increased%20my%20personal%20property%20coverage%20to%20a%20more%20appropriate%20amount.%20The%20combination%20of%20a%20claim%20on%20my%20record%20and%20higher%20personal%20property%20coverage%20costs%20me%20more%20in%20premiums%2C%20but%20it's%20worth%20it%20to%20me%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E2.%20An%20emergency%20fund%20is%20a%20must%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20insurance%20claim%20takes%20time.%20It%20could%20be%20months%20before%20you%20receive%20your%20full%20settlement%2C%20and%20as%20a%20result%2C%20you%20will%20have%20to%20pay%20some%20expenses%20out%20of%20pocket%20and%20submit%20receipts%20for%20reimbursement.%20In%20my%20case%2C%20I%20stayed%20in%20a%20hotel%20for%20the%20first%20two%20weeks.%20My%20insurance%20covered%20my%20relocation%20expenses.%20At%20the%20hotel%2C%20I%20had%20to%20pay%20for%20eating%20out%20and%20doing%20laundry%20since%20I%20had%20no%20direct%20access%20to%20a%20kitchen%2C%20washer%2C%20or%20dryer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20realized%20I'd%20be%20in%20temporary%20housing%20for%20a%20while%2C%20and%20since%20I%20work%20from%20home%2C%20I%20opted%20to%20end%20my%20stay%20in%20an%20Airbnb.%20It%20was%20cheaper%20long-term%20than%20a%20hotel%20%E2%80%94%20which%20meant%20my%20living%20expense%20benefit%20lasted%20longer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20relocation%20company%20only%20allowed%20direct%20billing%20for%20hotels%2C%20so%20I%20had%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20Airbnb%20upfront.%20I%20paid%20thousands%20out%20of%20pocket%20before%20getting%20reimbursed.%20Thankfully%2C%20I%20had%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-is-an-emergency-fund%5C%22%3Eemergency%20fund%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20I%20started%20years%20ago%20for%20these%20unforeseen%20scenarios.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E3.%20Document%2C%20document%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20process%20my%20claim%2C%20I%20had%20to%20submit%20documentation%20of%20everything%20damaged%20or%20destroyed.%20The%20more%20details%2C%20especially%20for%20valuable%20items%2C%20the%20faster%20your%20claim%20is%20processed.%20I%20was%20fortunate%20to%20have%20access%20to%20my%20damaged%20items.%20I%20started%20by%20recording%20a%20video%20of%20the%20damage%20and%20all%20my%20belongings.%20I%20talked%20throughout%20the%20video%2C%20opening%20drawers%2C%20closets%2C%20and%20cabinets.%20I%20also%20took%20photos%20of%20high-cost%20items%20to%20provide%20evidence%20of%20their%20value.%20I%20used%20the%20recording%20to%20make%20an%20itemized%20list%20of%20what%20needed%20to%20be%20replaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20making%20your%20list%2C%20make%20sure%20to%20include%20a%20detailed%20description%20of%20the%20item%2C%20date%20acquired%2C%20and%20purchase%20price%20(with%20copies%20of%20receipts%20if%20you%20have%20them).%20If%20you%20have%20a%20video%20and%20photos%20to%20accompany%20the%20list%2C%20it's%20helpful%20to%20include%20the%20room%20or%20location%20of%20each%20item.%20In%20addition%2C%20be%20sure%20to%20keep%20receipts%20from%20any%20expenses%20you%20incur%20along%20the%20way%20so%20you%20can%20submit%20them%20for%20reimbursement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E4.%20Your%20payments%20come%20in%20stages%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20renters%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-homeowners-insurance-companies%5C%22%3Ehomeowners%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E%20policies%2C%20you%20can%20insure%20your%20personal%20property%20for%20replacement%20cost%20value%20or%20actual%20cash%20value%20(replacement%20cost%20value%20minus%20depreciation).%20Since%20I%20had%20replacement%20cost%20coverage%2C%20I%20assumed%20that%20I%20would%20receive%20a%20single%20check%20for%20the%20total%20value%20of%20items%20lost.%20My%20insurance%20initially%20paid%20only%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20claim%20and%20held%20back%20an%20amount%20known%20as%20recoverable%20depreciation.%20Once%20I%20could%20show%20that%20I%20used%20the%20money%20to%20buy%20new%20items%2C%20I%20received%20a%20second%20payment%20for%20the%20balance.%20This%20is%20to%20prevent%20insurance%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20don't%20have%20to%20replace%20every%20item%20you%20lost.%20You%20can%20receive%20the%20total%20claim%20as%20long%20as%20you%20show%20that%20you%20used%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20the%20insurance%20payment%20to%20purchase%20new%20items.%20If%20you%20have%20to%20relocate%20temporarily%20and%20receive%20reimbursements%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.travelers.com%2Fclaims%2Fguides%2Floss-of-use-claim-expenses%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadditional%20living%20expenses%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20those%20payments%20might%20also%20come%20over%20time%20as%20you%20incur%20the%20costs%20and%20submit%20receipts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E5.%20Give%20yourself%20grace%20and%20time%20to%20adjust%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMoving%20is%20already%20a%20stressful%20and%20emotional%20experience%2C%20but%20moving%20with%20no%20notice%20and%20losing%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20your%20belongings%20is%20traumatic.%20At%20times%2C%20getting%20things%20in%20order%20felt%20like%20a%20full-time%20job.%20Plus%2C%20some%20unexpected%20events%20delayed%20the%20process.%20My%20insurance%20adjuster%20got%20COVID-19%20and%20was%20out%20of%20work%20for%20a%20while.%20The%20person%20I%20hired%20to%20move%20items%20into%20storage%20got%20in%20a%20car%20accident%2C%20so%20I%20postponed%20the%20moving%20date.%20Months%20later%2C%20I'm%20still%20dealing%20with%20being%20displaced%2C%20putting%20things%20in%20storage%2C%20replacing%20belongings%2C%20finding%20a%20new%20place%20to%20live%2C%20and%20unpacking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20learned%20to%20prioritize%20self-care%20and%20give%20myself%20grace%20as%20I%20caught%20up%20with%20work%20and%20restored%20my%20personal%20life.%20I'm%20forever%20grateful%20for%20friends%20and%20family%20who%20stepped%20in%20to%20help%20and%20clients%20who%20remain%20patient%20as%20I%20work%20to%20get%20caught%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20wants%20to%20think%20of%20the%20unthinkable%2C%20but%20the%20reality%20is%20that%20unexpected%20events%20take%20place.%20We%20must%20be%20prepared%20to%20protect%20our%20belongings%20and%2C%20frankly%2C%20our%20sanity.%20Getting%20through%20a%20disaster%20takes%20a%20lot%20of%20patience%20and%20time.%20Align%20yourself%20with%20resources%20upfront%20so%20you%20can%20get%20back%20on%20your%20feet%20and%20resume%20normalcy%20in%20due%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20published%20in%20June%202023.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirst-renters-insurance-claim-lessons-2024-03%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710239342000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64889d8162d3f10019967d05%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirst-renters-insurance-claim-lessons-2024-03%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20her%20apartment%20flooded%2C%20she%20was%20glad%20to%20have%20renters%20insurance%20%E2%80%94%20but%20she%20didn't%20have%20enough.%20After%20that%20first%20claim%2C%20she's%20learned%20a%20few%20things.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Chloe%20A.%20Moore)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirst-renters-insurance-claim-lessons-2024-03%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Why%20BJP%20Is%20Friendlier%20Than%20Ever%20With%20Regional%20Parties%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fcd6vo23_modi-rally-1200-_625x300_07_May_23.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-chandrababu-naidu-pawan-kalyan-alliance-finalised-say-sources-5200124%5C%22%3EBharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20in%20an%20alliance-forging%20mode%20for%20the%20past%20several%20months.%20Its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fin-andhras-tdp-bjp-alliance-stakes-are-higher-for-naidu-5217372%5C%22%3Erecent%20pacts%20with%20Chandrababu%20Naidu-led%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Pawan%20Kalyan's%20Jana%20Sena%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20made%20headlines.%20Considerable%20news%20space%20is%20also%20being%20expended%20on%20the%20possibility%20of%20the%20party%20striking%20up%20an%20electoral%20understanding%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftalks-with-naveen-patnaiks-party-stall-bjp-eyes-solo-contest-in-odisha-5204331%5C%22%3EBiju%20Janata%20Dal%20(BJD)%20in%20Odisha%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Weeks%20ago%2C%20the%20party%20stitched%20up%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20'ally-once-again'%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2-deputies-from-bjp-6-ministers-meet-nitish-kumars-new-bihar-team-4951298%5C%22%3ENitish%20Kumar%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20his%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20(JD-U).%20The%20BJP%20has%20also%20weaned%20the%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%20(RLD)%20led%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frld-bjp-alliance-jayant-chaudhary-news-had-limited-time-to-make-decision-rld-leader-on-bjp-alliance-buzz-5044098%5C%22%3EJayant%20Chaudhary%3C%2Fa%3E%20away%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-bjp-should-not-ignore-sp-congress-alliance-5111410%5C%22%3ESamajwadi%20Party-led%20opposition%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20aforementioned%20decisions%20were%20announced%20sequentially%20at%20different%20centres%2C%20the%20BJP%20leaders%20present%20took%20care%20to%20present%20a%20picture%20of%20humility.%20They%20ensured%20that%20the%20new%20ally%20was%20seen%20as%20being%20treated%20equally%2C%20although%20the%20reality%20was%20the%20opposite.%20The%20BJP%20remains%20the%20'Big%20B'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Changed%20Outlook%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20current%20disposition%20is%20at%20odds%20with%20its%20temperament%20last%20year%20in%20May%2C%20when%20it%20more%20or%20less%20glossed%20over%20the%2025th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA).%20It%20instead%20highlighted%20the%20ninth%20anniversary%20of%20the%20Modi%20government's%20formation.%20The%20reasons%20were%20not%20difficult%20to%20seek.%20Numerically%2C%20the%20BJP%20stopped%20being%20dependent%20on%20coalition%20partners%20in%202014%2C%20and%20in%20Prime%20Minister%20Nardendra%20Modi%2C%20it%20had%20a%20leader%20who%20towered%20over%20peers%20in%20any%20party%20in%20terms%20of%20popularity%20and%20charisma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompared%20to%20the%20previous%20NDA%20governments%20which%20had%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20as%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20paid%20scant%20attention%20to%20the%20concerns%20of%20its%20alliance%20partners.%20The%20phrase%20%26quot%3Bcompulsions%20of%20coalition%20politics%26quot%3B%2C%20which%20Manmohan%20Singh%20confessed%20restricted%20his%20decision-making%20abilities%2C%20applied%20equally%20to%20Vajpayee%20too.%20The%20BJP%2C%20between%201998%20and%202004%2C%20jettisoned%20its%20core%20issues%20-%20Ram%20temple%2C%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%20and%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20-%20from%20the%20National%20Agenda%20of%20Governance%2C%20which%20was%20adopted%20by%20coalition%20partners%20as%20the%20regime's%20consensual%20programme%20in%20March%201998.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20Government's%20Accommodative%20Stance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Modi%20government%20faced%20no%20such%20constraint.%20Its%20survival%20was%20never%20a%20worry.%20Contrarily%2C%20partners%20became%20more%20cautious%20for%20fear%20of%20losing%20their%20positions.%20From%20the%20beginning%2C%20especially%20after%202019%2C%20there%20were%20no%20'taboo'%20issues%20and%20many%20decisions%20that%20once%20appeared%20improbable%20were%20hustled%20through%20Parliament%20-%20the%20triple%20talaq%20bill%2C%20the%20status%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Bill%20(CAA)%2C%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20the%20Ram%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%20has%20changed%20between%20May%2015%2C%202023%2C%20the%20NDA's%2025th%20anniversary%2C%20and%20now%2C%20for%20the%20BJP%20to%20become%20more%20accommodative%20towards%20allies%3F%20Why%20the%20urgency%20to%20forge%20electoral%20alliances%2C%20with%20the%20total%20number%20of%20coalition%20partners%20now%20being%20the%20highest%20ever%3F%20Does%20the%20BJP's%20patience%20in%20exploring%20pacts%20with%20regional%20parties%20indicate%20the%20leadership's%20anxiety%20about%20electoral%20prospects%3F%20Or%2C%20should%20this%20be%20seen%20as%20evidence%20of%20a%20strategy%20of%20leaving%20no%20stone%20unturned%20in%20pursuit%20of%20its%20goal%2C%20ensuring%20that%20no%20uncertainty%20remained%3F%20And%20on%20the%20other%20end%2C%20do%20hurried%20alliances%20with%20the%20BJP%20indicate%20regional%20parties'%20fear%20of%20marginalisation%20unless%20they%20become%20part%20of%20the%20Big%20B%20team%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Partners%20Come%20And%20Go'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20India%20being%20a%20multi-party%20democracy%2C%20political%20parties%20have%20traditionally%20not%20forged%20alliances%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20principles.%20I%20was%20fortunate%20to%20ask%20Modi%20a%20question%20or%20two%20about%20NDA's%20alliances%20when%20I%20was%20researching%20for%20the%20biography%20I%20wrote%20on%20him.%20In%20the%20summer%20of%202012%2C%20when%20the%20number%20of%20NDA's%20allies%20was%20abysmally%20low%2C%20I%20asked%20him%20how%20the%20party%20could%20win%20back%20estranged%20partners.%20He%20said%20when%20the%20party%20first%20formed%20a%20government%20in%201996%2C%20it%20got%20no%20partners%20except%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20the%20Akali%20Dal%2C%20and%2C%20as%20a%20result%2C%20the%20government%20bowed%20out%20of%20office%20in%20thirteen%20days.%20But%20in%201998%2C%20the%20party%20secured%20more%20pre-poll%20partners%20(and%20several%20more%20after%20elections)%20because%20its%20%26quot%3Bwinnability%26quot%3B%20was%20greater.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20said%20partners%20%26quot%3Bcome%20and%20go%26quot%3B%20because%20of%20their%20assessment%20of%20the%20BJP's%20winnability.%20%26quot%3BIf%20allies%20become%20confident%20that%20by%20associating%20with%20the%20BJP%20they%20will%20win%20more%20seats%2C%20they%20will%20come%20and%20join%20the%20BJP.%20But%20if%20they%20think%20we%20are%20a%20burden%20and%20that%20they%20will%20save%20a%20few%20seats%20by%20contesting%20on%20its%20own%2C%20then%20they%20will%20not%20ally%20with%20the%20BJP.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClearly%2C%20according%20to%20Modi%2C%20the%20BJP's%20own%20attitude%20towards%20allies%20depended%20on%20their%20assessment%20of%20the%20potential%20partner's%20prospects%20-%20on%20whether%20the%20party%20was%20on%20a%20strong%20wicket%20in%20the%20home%20state%20or%20region.%20The%20electoral%20strength%20of%20regional%20parties%20traditionally%20determines%20their%20equation%20with%20national%20parties%20-%20for%20instance%2C%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20regional%20parties%20have%20since%20the%20late%201960s%20been%20the%20leaders%20of%20alliances%2C%20and%20the%20national%20players%20(the%20Congress%20previously%2C%20and%20now%20the%20BJP)%20take%20the%20back%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIdeology%20No%20Bar%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20beginning%2C%20ideology%20played%20little%20role%20in%20political%20partnerships.%20Initially%20after%20independence%2C%20when%20the%20Congress%20was%20the%20nationally%20dominant%20party%2C%20anti-Congressism%20acted%20as%20the%20glue.%20In%20May%201963%2C%20major%20ideologically%20disparate%20opposition%20parties%2C%20including%20the%20Bharatiya%20Jana%20Sangh%20(BJS)%2C%20jointly%20contested%20four%20Lok%20Sabha%20by-elections%20against%20the%20Congress%2C%20as%20an%20experiment.%20The%20trial%20was%20a%20success%20for%20they%20won%20three%20seats.%20In%20four%20years%2C%20this%20evolved%20into%20the%20Samyukya%20Vidhayak%20Dal%20(SVD)%20coalition%20governments%20in%20several%20states.%20This%20was%20the%20first%20experience%20with%20coalitions%2C%20and%20although%20they%20collapsed%20soon%2C%20a%20new%20era%20in%20Indian%20politics%20was%20heralded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20BJP%20or%20the%20preceding%20BJS%2C%20alliances%20were%20formed%20solely%20to%20enhance%20collective%20winnability.%20Like%20in%201977%2C%20when%20all%20non-Left%20opposition%20parties%20united%20and%20defeated%20Indira%20Gandhi.%20They%20joined%20forces%20in%201989%20too%20to%20defeat%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%2C%20even%20though%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20and%20other%20regional%20partners-including%20the%20Left-were%20ideologically%20hostile%20to%20one%20another.%20Anti-Congressism%20brought%20them%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Disintegration%20Of%20INDIA%20Bloc%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20in%20contrast%2C%20finds%20it%20problematic%20when%20non-BJP%20parties%20from%20different%20ideological%20stables%20get%20together%2C%20as%20it%20happened%20with%20the%20I.N.D.I.A%20alliance.%20This%20prompts%20us%20to%20assess%20the%20reasons%20behind%20the%20change%20in%20the%20BJP's%20outlook%20towards%20alliances%20between%20last%20May%20and%20today.%20The%20party's%20revived%20interest%20in%20regional%20and%20even%20sub-regional%20parties%20had%20initially%20to%20do%20with%20opposition%20parties%20trying%20to%20maximise%20their%20Lok%20Sabha%20wins%20with%20one-on-one%20contests%2C%20with%20a%20single%20opposition%20candidate%20taking%20on%20the%20BJP%20nominee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20stage%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20even%20tried%20to%20outnumber%20the%20opposition%20bloc%20by%20getting%20smaller%20parties%20on%20board.%20And%20it%20did%20not%20change%20tack%20even%20after%20the%20I.N.D.I.A%20bloc%20itself%20started%20seeing%20fissures.%20That%20was%20when%20Modi%20decided%20to%20set%20the%20audacious%20victory%20target%20of%20370%20seats%20for%20the%20BJP%20and%20400-plus%20for%20the%20NDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EQuestion%20Of%20'Winnability'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20clear%20that%20the%20BJP%20wishes%20to%20have%20as%20many%20parties%20as%20possible%20in%20the%20NDA%2C%20especially%20those%20like%20the%20TDP%2C%20which%20it%20feels%20has%20better%20'winnability'%20now%20than%20earlier.%20Unlike%20what%20Modi%20told%20me%2C%20today%20it%20is%20not%20only%20the%20allies%20who%20make%20a%20beeline%20for%20the%20BJP%20if%20they%20think%20their%20prospects%20would%20improve%20-%20the%20BJP%2C%20too%2C%20is%20wooing%20smaller%20parties%20when%20it%20stands%20to%20gain%2C%20especially%20in%20states%20where%20they%20are%20not%20a%20dominant%20force.%20Barring%20odd%20exceptions%2C%20the%20BJP's%20ties%20with%20its%20allies%20are%20based%20on%20political%20pragmatism%20today.%20It's%20a%20sea%20change%20from%20the%20L.K.%20Advani%20era%2C%20when%20the%20BJP%20basked%20under%20'splendid-isolation'.%20Paradoxically%2C%20of%20the%20two%20oldest%20partners%20of%20the%20BJP%20-%20the%20Akali%20Dal%20and%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20-%20one%20is%20not%20with%20the%20NDA%20anymore%2C%20while%20the%20other%20is%20represented%20by%20one%20of%20the%20factions%20that%20were%20formed%20after%20a%20bitter%20parting%2C%20aided%20in%20no%20small%20measure%20by%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20dominant%20character%20is%20unlikely%20to%20get%20diluted%20unless%20its%20tally%20takes%20a%20significant%20beating.%20Consequently%2C%20its%20allies%20face%20the%20risk%20of%20getting%20co-opted%20into%20the%20BJP%20or%20facing%20an%20over-bearing%20partner.%20In%20Maharashtra%2C%20ties%20soured%20with%20the%20united%20Shiv%20Sena%20because%20the%20BJP%20sought%20dominance%20over%20its%20partners.%20Likewise%2C%20sub-regional%20parties%20stand%20the%20risk%20of%20getting%20subsumed%20within%20the%20BJP%20if%20just%20a%20few%20leaders%20cross%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20alliances%20are%20formed%20with%20a%20programmatic%20agreement%20-%20was%20the%20TDP%20aware%20that%20CAA%20rules%20would%20be%20notified%3F%20Or%2C%20has%20the%20Congress%20discussed%20the%20promises%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20been%20serially%20making%3F%20No%20alliance%20is%20'committed'%20to%20principles%20or%20ideology%2C%20and%20so%2C%20they%20remain%20transitory%2C%20changing%20from%20election%20to%20election.%20Every%20party%20will%20continue%20making%20choices%20solely%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20improving%20its%20own%20'winnability'.%20We%20will%20know%20in%20possibly%20just%20two%20and%20a%20half%20months%20if%20siding%20with%20the%20NDA%20increased%20their%20collective%20'winnability'%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENilanjan%20Mukhopadhyay%20is%20a%20journalist%20and%20author.%20His%20books%20include%20'The%20Demolition%2C%20The%20Verdict'%20and%20'The%20Temple%3A%20The%20Definitive%20Book%20on%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20Project'.%20He%20also%20wrote%20'Narendra%20Modi%3A%20The%20Man%20The%20Times'%2C%20and%20'The%20RSS%3A%20Icons%20of%20the%20Indian%20Right'%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20'%3Cem%3ESikhs%3A%20Untold%20Agony%20of%201984'%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710239280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fcd6vo23_modi-rally-1200-_625x300_07_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-b