ggression%20it%20boasts%20of%2C%20their%20batting%20remained%20painfully%20out%20of%20depth%20for%20the%20better%20part%20of%20the%20five%20Tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proverbial%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FBazball%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBazball%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20a%20neologism%20coined%20by%20%3Cem%3EESPNCricinfo%3C%2Fem%3E%20journalist%20Andrew%20Miller%20to%20describe%20the%20new%20brand%20of%20Test%20cricket%20England%20have%20adopted%20under%20the%20current%20regime%20%E2%80%93%20spectacularly%20folded%20against%20a%20time-tested%2C%20seasoned%2C%20and%20uncomplicated%20method%20of%20winning%20Test%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20England%20decided%20to%20metamorphosise%20their%20Test%20setup%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202022%20after%20a%20long%20streak%20of%20underwhelming%20results%2C%20it%20was%20about%20a%20shift%20in%20mindset%20and%20less%20about%20a%20change%20in%20personnel.%20Former%20New%20Zealand%20captain%20Brendon%20McCullum%20was%20brought%20in%20to%20oversee%20this%20transition%20while%20the%20captaincy%20mantle%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20Ben%20Stokes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlaying%20in%20an%20unusually%20aggressive%20manner%20was%20critical%20to%20the%20philosophy%20this%20new%20regime%20employed%2C%20even%20if%2C%20at%20times%20it%20came%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20some%20key%20fundamentals.%20Playing%20a%20long-drawn%2C%20attritional%20game%20was%20suddenly%20so%20last-season%20and%20those%20not%20willing%20to%20mend%20their%20ways%20were%20no%20longer%20welcome%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMcCullum%E2%80%99s%20own%20Test%20career%20in%20fact%20had%20been%20characterised%20by%20this%20approach.%20He%20never%20boasted%20of%20the%20strongest%20defence%20but%20more%20than%20made%20up%20for%20it%20with%20inventive%20strokeplay%20and%20a%20higher%20willingness%20to%20take%20risks%20than%20most%20players%20would.%20He%E2%80%99d%20never%20coached%20a%20Test%20side%20before%20landing%20the%20high-profile%20job%20at%20England.%20His%20coaching%20stints%20were%20limited%20to%20T20%20franchises%20but%20perhaps%20that%E2%80%99s%20exactly%20what%20England%20were%20after%20%E2%80%93%20a%20change%20in%20optics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMcCullum%20brought%20with%20him%20a%20personality%20that%20was%20easily%20identifiable%20to%20the%20narrative%20spin%20that%20England%20were%20looking%20for%20after%20a%20prolonged%20period%20of%20mediocrity.%20Add%20to%20it%20Stokes%E2%80%99s%20reputation%20for%20being%20a%20%3Cem%3Eman%20who%20stood%20up%20in%20the%20big%20moments%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20you%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20asked%20for%20two%20more%20saleable%20names%20to%20make%20a%20transformative%20idea%20float.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20surface%2C%20there%20was%20nothing%20to%20not%20love%20about%20the%20new%20approach.%20It%20was%20indeed%20refreshing%20and%20constantly%20engaging.%20There%20was%20palpable%20urgency%20in%20how%20England%20batted.%20Run%20scoring%20was%20brisk.%20Every%20single%20member%20in%20the%20squad%20completely%20bought%20into%20the%20idea%20and%20showed%20little%20hesitance%20in%20embracing%20the%20additional%20risks%20it%20demanded%20taken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20inherent%20nature%20of%20Test%20cricket%20still%20requires%20a%20team%20to%20be%20abundantly%20resourceful%20to%20take%2020%20wickets.%20There%E2%80%99s%20no%20substitute%20to%20this.%20Other%20than%20in%20those%20weather-affected%20condensed%20Tests%20where%20teams%20are%20desperately%20trying%20to%20force%20a%20result%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20imperative%20to%20bowl%20teams%20out%20twice%20in%20order%20to%20win.%20An%20overlooked%20aspect%20in%20England%E2%80%99s%20early%20success%20during%20the%20%3Cem%3EBazball%20%3C%2Fem%3Eera%20was%20their%20bowling%20attack%20kept%20achieving%20this%20with%20remarkable%20consistency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBazball%3C%2Fem%3E%20won%20its%20validation%20among%20fans%20and%20media%20alike%20through%20Jonny%20Bairstow%20and%20Joe%20Root%E2%80%99s%20audacious%20batting%20in%20the%202022%20summer.%20It%20was%20in%20all%20honesty%20nothing%20like%20anything%20anyone%20had%20ever%20seen.%20England%20were%20reversing%20every%20tenet%20that%20was%20considered%20sacred%20to%20Test%20batting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20adverse%20conditions%20and%20against%20stronger%20oppositions%2C%20the%20exuberance%20with%20the%20bat%20was%20only%20going%20to%20take%20them%20so%20far%20unless%20they%20built%20the%20bowling%20muscle%20to%20compete.%20And%20this%20is%20precisely%20where%20Rahul%20Dravid%20and%20Rohit%20Sharma%E2%80%99s%20India%20bled%20them%20dry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20saw%20no%20reason%20to%20be%20rattled%20by%20the%20storm%20England%20meant%20to%20throw%20at%20them.%20Sure%2C%20the%20Ben%20Ducketts%20and%20the%20Ollie%20Popes%20of%20the%20world%20would%20keep%20manufacturing%20low-percentage%20shots%20and%20even%20execute%20them%20with%20more%20success%20than%20an%20average%20player%20would.%20In%20the%20end%20though%2C%20the%20quality%20and%20depth%20in%20bowling%20resources%20would%20tilt%20the%20scale%20India%E2%80%99s%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEngland%E2%80%99s%20bowlers%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20were%20no%20match%20for%20India%20on%20either%20front.%20Their%20seamers%20were%20old%20and%20fragile%2C%20while%20their%20rookie%20spinners%20%E2%80%93%20despite%20promise%20%E2%80%93%20were%20out%20of%20their%20element%20for%20the%20most%20part.%20The%20additional%20hilt%20with%20the%20bat%20was%20never%20going%20to%20make%20up%20for%20this%20glaring%20shortcoming%20in%20their%20squad.%20But%20Stokes%20and%20McCullum%20never%20once%20compromised%20on%20batting%20cushion%20in%20pushing%20for%20a%20win.%20Underneath%20the%20veneer%20of%20positivity%20and%20gung-ho%20aggression%2C%20England%20actually%20played%20it%20quite%20safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20this%20invalidates%20the%20decisive%20shift%20in%20approach%20that%20they%E2%80%99ve%20made%20since%20the%20coming%20together%20of%20the%20current%20leadership%20group.%20They%E2%80%99ve%20truly%20played%20an%20enthralling%20brand%20of%20cricket%20and%20has%20indeed%20gotten%20more%20people%20glued%20to%20their%20TV%20screens%20than%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20so%20far%2C%20barring%20an%20exceptional%20whitewash%20of%20Pakistan%20away%20from%20home%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20only%20accomplished%20what%20should%20be%20deemed%20the%20bare%20minimum%20for%20a%20team%20for%20their%20resources.%20Of%20the%20two%20biggest%20overseas%20assignments%20in%20the%20game%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20yet%20to%20take%20one%20and%20have%20been%20thoroughly%20clobbered%20in%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20getting%20comprehensively%20beaten%20in%20India%20is%20rather%20on%20expected%20lines%20for%20any%20visiting%20team%20barring%20Australia.%20It%20certainly%20is%20no%20declaration%20of%20failure%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3EBazball%3C%2Fem%3E%20project.%20But%20given%20the%20nauseatingly%20self-indulgent%20discourse%20the%20English%20commentariat%20has%20built%20around%20%3Cem%3EBazball%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20perhaps%20a%20little%20grounding%20if%20not%20outright%20humbling%20was%20long%20overdue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanctimony%20and%20self-righteousness%20were%20never%20the%20most%20unfamiliar%20traits%20to%20English%20cricket.%20But%20they%E2%80%99ve%20scaled%20new%20heights%20in%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%20as%20the%20current%20team%20management%20have%20allegedly%20taken%20it%20upon%20themselves%20to%20save%2C%20revive%2C%20reinvigorate%2C%20redefine%2C%20reinvent%2C%20and%20while%20they%E2%80%99re%20at%20it%2C%20maybe%20even%20rebirth%20Test%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20%3Cem%3EBazball%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20renaissance%20that%20will%20make%20Test%20matches%20entertaining%2C%20we%20must%20be%20reminded%20every%20time%20the%20camera%20pans%20on%20Stokes.%20Every%20time%20Stokes%20makes%20a%20bowling%20change%2C%20or%20opts%20for%20a%20funky-looking%20field%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.espncricinfo.com%2Fstory%2Feng-vs-aus-1st-test-edgbaston-stokes-defends-controversial-declaration-as-england-s-chance-to-pounce-on-australia-1382520%5C%22%3Eprematurely%20declares%3C%2Fa%3E%20an%20innings%20for%20no%20apparent%20gain%2C%20it%20must%20be%20acknowledged%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20being%20done%20to%20safeguard%20the%20future%20of%20Test%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fthe-ishan-kishan-shreyas-iyer-fiasco-will-bcci-ever-come-clean%5C%22%3EThe%C2%A0Ishan%C2%A0Kishan-Shreyas%20Iyer%20Fiasco%3A%20Will%20BCCI%20Ever%20Come%20Clean%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELawrence%20Booth%2C%20the%20editor%20of%20Wisden%20has%20already%20co-authored%20a%20book%20called%20%E2%80%98Bazball%E2%80%99%20that%20claims%20to%20tell%20the%20inside%20story%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98Test%20Cricket%20Revolution%E2%80%99.%20The%20revolution%20the%20book%20wants%20to%20talk%20about%20had%20at%20the%20time%20of%20its%20publishing%20failed%20to%20win%20the%20Ashes%20at%20home%20and%20was%20yet%20to%20embark%20on%20a%20tour%20of%20India%20or%20Australia.%20Nonetheless%2C%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20the%20authors%20from%20shaming%20the%20two%20most%20successful%20modern%20era%20Test%20teams%20for%20not%20replicating%20England%E2%80%99s%20approach%20already.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20citing%20an%20instance%20of%20India%20playing%20a%20Test%20in%20the%20Caribbean%20in%202023%2C%20the%20book%20raises%20concerns%20over%20the%20uninspiring%20strike%20rates%20at%20which%20star%20Indian%20batters%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20Virat%20Kohli%20were%20%3Cem%3Echugging%20along%3C%2Fem%3E.%20In%20a%202024%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.msn.com%2Fen-gb%2Fsport%2Fcricket%2Fmail-sport-s-cricket-wishlist-for-2024%2Far-AA1m7rra%5C%22%3Ewishlist%20piece%20for%20Daily%20Mail%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Booth%20expresses%20his%20disappointment%20at%20Australia%E2%80%99s%20unlikeliness%20to%20%3Cem%3Etake%20a%20leaf%20out%20of%20the%20Poms%E2%80%99%20book%3C%2Fem%3E%20with%20their%20middle%20order%20mainstays%20Steve%20Smith%20and%20Marnus%20Labuschagne%20%3Cem%3Eoperating%20in%20their%20own%20bubble%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESmith%2C%20Kohli%2C%20Labuschagne%2C%20and%20Sharma%20are%20among%20the%20finest%20batters%20in%20the%20modern%20game%20and%20boast%20of%20an%20infinitely%20superior%20career%20to%20every%20current%20England%20batter%20bar%20Joe%20Root.%20But%20the%20four%20must%20still%20mend%20their%20ways%20and%20play%20a%20game%20that%20satisfies%20the%20idea%20the%20English%20have%20decided%20to%20rally%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20overzealous%20and%20fervent%20coverage%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20quite%20matter%20on%20its%20own.%20The%20English%20press%20is%20quite%20famous%20for%20it%20and%20rather%20prides%20itself%20in%20being%20wind-up%20merchants%20of%20sorts.%20Except%20the%20England%20players%20too%20actively%20do%20their%20bit%20in%20peddling%20puffery%20around%20the%20cult%20of%20%3Cem%3EBazball%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefeats%20under%20this%20regime%20have%20been%20explained%20away%20by%20players%20themselves%20as%20insignificant%20as%20long%20as%20the%20style%20of%20play%20is%20not%20compromised.%20After%20Australia%20pulled%20an%20incredible%20heist%20at%20Edgbaston%20in%20the%20opening%20Ashes%20Test%20last%20year%2C%20McCullum%20practically%20implied%20it%20was%20in%20fact%20England%E2%80%99s%20fast-paced%20approach%20that%20left%20enough%20time%20for%20Australia%20to%20force%20a%20win.%20In%20McCullum%E2%80%99s%20heady%20imaginations%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smh.com.au%2Fsport%2Fcricket%2Fit-feels-like-we-ve-won-the-wit-and-wisden-of-robinson-and-england-20230623-p5diun.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eit%20felt%20like%20they%E2%80%99d%20won%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20one%20step%20ahead%20from%20his%20coach%2C%20Stokes%20in%20fact%20dismissed%20the%20idea%20of%20his%20team%20affording%20a%20p