com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FDynamic-Ally-Pictures.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235939178%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Media%20and%20content%20powerhouse%20Banijay%20has%20launched%20joint%20venture%20Dynamic%20Ally%20Pictures%20in%20Germany%2C%20further%20expanding%20its%20scripted%20capacity%20in%20the%20country.%20The%20Berlin-based%20production%20company%2C%20founded%20and%20led%20by%C2%A0%E2%80%9CHelgoland%20513%E2%80%9D%C2%A0executive%20producers%20Veronica%20Priefer%20and%20Johannes%20Kunkel%2C%20is%20dedicated%20to%20developing%2C%20packaging%20and%20distributing%20scripted%20content%20for%20the%20German%20and%20international%20market.%20Priefer%20and%20Kunkel%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Leo%20Barraclough%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fglobal%2Fbanijay-helgoland-513-veronica-priefer-johannes-kunkel-1235939178%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fglobal%2Fbanijay-helgoland-513-veronica-priefer-johannes-kunkel-1235939178%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fglobal%2Fbanijay-helgoland-513-veronica-priefer-johannes-kunkel-1235939178%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20FAQs%20on%20Electoral%20Bonds%2C%20SBI's%20Beneficial%20Ownership%20Proformas%20Disappear%20from%20Website%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F05105750%2F1166496076_ac2efae08c_c.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20refused%20to%20grant%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20extra%20time%20to%20furnish%20information%20about%20the%20buyers%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20(EBs)%20and%20the%20political%20parties%20that%20redeemed%20them.%20Instead%2C%20the%20court%20threatened%20the%20bank%20with%20penal%20action%20if%20it%20continued%20to%20defy%20its%20orders%2C%20leaving%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20largest%20bank%20facing%20consequences%20it%20deserved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20its%20website%2C%20SBI%20proudly%20proclaims%20itself%20as%20a%20Fortune%20500%20company%20with%20a%20rich%20heritage%20and%20legacy%20of%20over%20200%20years%2C%20boasting%20a%2025%25%20market%20share%20and%20serving%20over%20480%20million%20customers%20through%20a%20vast%20network%20of%2022%2C000-plus%20branches%20and%20more%20than%2065%2C600%20ATMs.%20However%2C%20inexplicably%2C%20this%20public%20sector%20banking%20behemoth%20adopted%20the%20%E2%80%98Please%20miss%2C%20my%20dog%20ate%20my%20homework%20miss%E2%80%99%20style%20of%20argument%20while%20pleading%20its%20inability%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20transparency%20directives%20of%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20a%20five-judge%20constitution%20bench%20of%20the%20court%20reiterated%20the%20fundamental%20right%20of%20every%20voter%20to%20know%20all%20information%20that%20is%20essential%20to%20make%20an%20informed%20choice%20on%20the%20polling%20day.%20This%20right%20covers%20details%20of%20who%20gives%20how%20much%20money%20to%20which%20political%20party%2C%20among%20other%20information%2C%20the%20court%20held%20unanimously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20burning%20the%20midnight%20oil%20to%20collate%20information%20on%20buyers%20and%20redeemers%20of%20EBs%20to%20hand%20over%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20for%20publication%20on%20its%20website%2C%20SBI%20requested%20an%20extension%20until%20the%20end%20of%20June%2C%20when%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20would%20be%20done%20and%20dusted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20conducted%20business%20with%20SBI%20for%20over%20a%20decade%20as%20a%20student%2C%20I%20am%20left%20questioning%20its%20assertion%20of%20being%20%E2%80%98the%20most%20trusted%20bank%20by%20Indians%20through%20generations%2C%E2%80%99%20especially%20in%20light%20of%20its%20excuse%20that%20it%20holds%20records%20about%20buyers%20and%20recipients%20of%20EBs%20in%20separate%20silos%2C%20claiming%20that%20matching%20the%20information%20between%20them%20is%20a%20time-consuming%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESix%20years%20ago%2C%20noted%20journalist%20Poonam%20Agarwal%20wrote%20an%20investigative%20piece%20to%20discover%20that%20every%20EB%20of%20every%20denomination%20has%20a%20unique%20identification%20number%20printed%20on%20it%20which%20is%20visible%20only%20under%20UV%20light.%20Is%20it%20not%20commonsensical%20to%20make%20the%20assumption%20that%20this%20unique%20number%20would%20be%20recorded%20against%20every%20denomination%20of%20EB%20sold%20to%20prospective%20donors%20and%20matched%20against%20every%20EB%20redeemed%20by%20political%20parties%3F%20This%20is%20an%20essential%20safeguard%20to%20prevent%20fake%20EBs%20from%20entering%20the%20system%2C%20especially%20in%20our%20country%20where%20counterfeiting%20currency%20notes%2C%20coins%20and%20stamp%20papers%20is%20almost%20like%20a%20cottage%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20would%20think%2C%20the%20digitalised%20banking%20processes%20of%20SBI%20would%20make%20matching%20of%20donor%20and%20redeemer%20data%20as%20easy%20as%20clicking%20a%20few%20buttons%20to%20let%20the%20computers%20spit%20out%20the%20nexus.%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20is%20not%20required%20for%20this%20exercise%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOr%20did%20we%20read%20much%20more%20than%20what%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20specifically%20recorded%20as%20directives%20to%20SBI%20and%20ECI%2C%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20its%20February%20judgment%3F%20Was%20our%20expectation%20of%20being%20able%20to%20discover%20who%20donated%20how%20much%20to%20which%20political%20party%20through%20the%20EB%20route%20unrealistic%3F%20For%20now%2C%20all%20that%20we%20will%20get%20to%20know%20from%20SBI%20through%20the%20ECI%20is%2C%20who%20bought%20EBs%20of%20which%20denomination%20and%20when%2C%20and%20the%20date%20and%20denomination-wise%20encashment%20of%20EBs%20by%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20directed%20SBI%20to%20disclose%20only%20this%20much%20in%20February.%20Yet%2C%20SBI%20was%20reluctant%20to%20disclose%20even%20this%20information%20until%20after%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20did%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20say%20about%20the%20voter%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20know%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESBI%E2%80%99s%20latest%20pleadings%20have%20actually%20brought%20to%20light%20a%20significant%20element%20of%20disconnect%20between%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20theory%20about%20the%20%E2%80%98voters%E2%80%99%20right%20to%20know%E2%80%99%20and%20the%20specific%20directives%20it%20gave%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20following%20extracts%20from%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20judgment%20summarise%20its%20well-constructed%20theory%20regarding%20the%20voter%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20know%2C%20based%20on%20existing%20case%20law%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CElectoral%20democracy%20in%20India%20is%20premised%20on%20the%20principle%20of%20political%20equality%20which%20the%20Constitution%20guarantees%20in%20two%20ways.%20First%2C%20by%20guaranteeing%20the%20principle%20of%20%E2%80%9Cone%20person%20one%20vote%E2%80%9D%20which%20assures%20equal%20representation%20in%20voting.%20The%20Constitution%20prescribes%20two%20conditions%20with%20respect%20to%20elections%20to%20seats%20in%20Parliament%20which%20guarantee%20the%20principle%20of%20%E2%80%9Cone%20person%20one%20vote%E2%80%9D%20with%20respect%20to%20every%20voter%20and%20amongst%20every%20State%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSecond%2C%20the%20Constitution%20ensures%20that%20socio-economic%20inequality%20does%20not%20perpetuate%20political%20inequality%20by%20mandating%20reservation%20of%20seats%20for%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20in%20Parliament%20and%20State%20Assemblies%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Constitution%20guarantees%20political%20equality%20by%20focusing%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98elector%E2%80%99%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98elected%E2%80%99.%20These%20two%20constitutional%20precepts%20foster%20political%20equality%20in%20the%20following%20two%20ways.%20First%2C%20the%20Constitution%20mandates%20that%20the%20value%20of%20each%20vote%20is%20equal.%20This%20guarantee%20ensures%20formal%20political%20equality%20where%20every%20person%E2%80%99s%20vote%20is%20accorded%20equal%20weightage.%20Second%2C%20the%20Constitution%20ensures%20that%20members%20of%20socially%20marginalized%20groups%20are%20not%20excluded%20from%20the%20political%20process.%20This%20guarantee%20ensures%20(a)%20equality%20in%20representation%3B%20and%20(b)%20equality%20in%20influence%20over%20political%20decisions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20political%20inequality%20continues%20to%20persist%20in%20spite%20of%20the%20constitutional%20guarantees.%20One%20of%20the%20factors%20which%20contributes%20to%20the%20inequality%20is%20the%20difference%20in%20the%20ability%20of%20persons%20to%20influence%20political%20decisions%20because%20of%20economic%20inequality.%20In%20a%20politically%20equal%20society%2C%20the%20citizens%20must%20have%20an%20equal%20voice%20to%20influence%20the%20political%20process.%20We%20have%20already%20in%20the%20preceding%20section%20elucidated%20the%20close%20association%20of%20money%20and%20politics%20where%20we%20explained%20the%20influence%20of%20money%20over%20electoral%20outcomes.%20However%2C%20the%20influence%20of%20money%20over%20electoral%20politics%20is%20not%20limited%20to%20its%20impact%20over%20electoral%20outcomes.%20It%20also%20spills%20over%20to%20governmental%20decisions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20must%20be%20recalled%20here%20that%20the%20legal%20regime%20in%20India%20does%20not%20distinguish%20between%20campaign%20funding%20and%20electoral%20funding.%20The%20money%20which%20is%20donated%20to%20political%20parties%20is%20not%20used%20by%20the%20political%20party%20only%20for%20the%20purposes%20of%20electoral%20campaign.%20Party%20donations%20are%20also%20used%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20to%20build%20offices%20for%20the%20political%20party%20and%20pay%20party%20workers.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20window%20for%20contributions%20is%20not%20open%20for%20a%20limited%20period%20only%20prior%20to%20the%20elections.%20Money%20can%20be%20contributed%20to%20political%20parties%20throughout%20the%20year%20and%20the%20contributed%20money%20can%20be%20spent%20by%20the%20political%20party%20for%20reasons%20other%20than%20just%20election%20campaigning.%20It%20is%20in%20light%20of%20the%20nexus%20between%20economic%20inequality%20and%20political%20inequality%2C%20and%20the%20legal%20regime%20in%20India%20regulating%20party%20financing%20that%20the%20essentiality%20of%20the%20information%20on%20political%20financing%20for%20an%20informed%20voter%20must%20be%20analyzed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fem%3EEconomic%20inequality%20leads%20to%20differing%20levels%20of%20political%20engagement%20because%20of%20the%20deep%20association%20between%20money%20and%20politics.%20At%20a%20primary%20level%2C%20political%20contributions%20give%20a%20%E2%80%9Cseat%20at%20the%20table%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20contributor.%20That%20is%2C%20it%20enhances%20access%20to%20legislators.%20This%20access%20also%20translates%20into%20influence%20over%20policy-making.%20An%20economically%20affluent%20person%20has%20a%20higher%20ability%20to%20make%20financial%20contributions%20to%20political%20parties%2C%20and%20there%20is%20a%20legitimate%20possibility%20that%20financial%20contribution%20to%20a%20political%20party%20would%20lead%20to%20quid%20pro%20quo%20arrangements%20because%20of%20the%20close%20nexus%20between%20money%20and%20politics.%20Quid%20pro%20quo%20arrangements%20could%20be%20in%20the%20form%20of%20introducing%20a%20policy%20change%2C%20or%20granting%20a%20license%20to%20the%20contributor.%20The%20money%20that%20is%20contributed%20could%20not%20only%20influence%20electoral%20outcomes%20but%20also%20policies%20particularly%20because%20contributions%20are%20not%20merely%20limited%20to%20the%20campaign%20or%20pre-campaign%20period.%20Financial%20contributions%20could%20be%20made%20even%20after%20a%20political%20party%20or%20coalition%20of%20parties%20form%20Government.%20The%20possibility%20of%20a%20quid%20pro%20quo%20arrangement%20in%20such%20situations%20is%20even%20higher.%20Information%20about%20political%20funding%20would%20enable%20a%20voter%20to%20assess%20if%20there%20is%20a%20correlation%20between%20policy%20making%20and%20financial%20contributions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20information%20on%20donor%20contributions%20to%20be%20relevant%20and%20essential%2C%20it%20is%20not%20necessary%20that%20voters%20have%20to%20take%20the%20initiative%20to%20peruse%20the%20list%20of%20contributors%20to%20find%20relevant%20information%20which%20would%20enable%20them%20to%20cast%20their%20vote%20effectively.%20Electronic%20and%20print%20media%20would%20present%20the%20information%20on%20contributions%20received%20by%20political%20parties%2C%20and%20the%20probable%20link%20between%20the%20contribution%20and%20the%20licenses%20which%20were%20given%20to%20the%20company%20in%20an%20accessible%20format.%20The%20responses%20to%20such%20information%20by%20the%20Government%20and%20political%20parties%20would%20go%20a%20long%20way%20in%20informing%20the%20voter%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20view%20of%20the%20above%20discussion%2C%20we%20are%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%20the%20information%20about%20funding%20to%20a%20political%20party%20is%20essential%20for%20a%20voter%20to%20exercise%20their%20freedom%20to%20vote%20in%20an%20effective%20manner.%20The%20Electoral%20Bond%20Scheme%20and%20the%20impugned%20provisions%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20they%20infringe%20upon%20the%20right%20to%20information%20of%20the%20voter%20by%20anonymizing%20contributions%20through%20electoral%20bonds%20are%20violative%20of%20Article%2019(1)(a).%E2%80%9D%20(emphasis%20supplied)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20above%20extracts%20taken%20from%20the%20February%202024%20judgment%20make%20it%20amply%20clear%20that%20the%20foundational%20basis%20of%20voters%E2%80%99%20right%20to%20know%20is%20not%20just%20the%20right%20to%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression%20guaranteed%20under%20Article%2019(1)(a)%20of%20the%20Constitution%20but%20also%20the%20necessity%20to%20create%20a%20level%20playing%20field%20for%20all%20kinds%20of%20voters%2C%20both%20haves%20and%20have-nots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETransparency%20of%20political%20party%20funding%20is%20essential%20to%20contain%2C%20if%20not%20completely%20eliminate%20the%20influence%20of%20moneybags%20on%20policymaking%20and%20other%20decisions%20of%20the%20government.%20The%20court%20did%20not%20stop%20at%20just%20that.%20It%20went%20on%20to%20compare%20the%20various%20legal%20modes%20of%20contributing%20funds%20to%20political%20parties%20in%20terms%20of%20degrees%20of%20transparency%20in%20the%20following%20words%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20these%20three%20methods%20of%20political%20contribution%20(electronic%20transfer%20other%20than%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20contribution%20to%20Electoral%20Trust%2C%20and%20Electoral%20Bonds)%20are%20placed%20on%20a%20continuum%2C%20transfer%20through%20electronic%20means%20(other%20than%20electoral%20bonds)%20would%20be%20placed%20on%20one%20end%20and%20Electoral%20Bonds%20would%20be%20placed%20on%20the%20other%20end.%20A%20voter%20would%20receive%20complete%20information%20about%20contributions%20made%20above%20twenty%20thousand%20to%20a%20political%20party%20in%20the%20case%20of%20electronic%20transfer%20made%20directly%20to%20a%20political%20party%20other%20than%20through%20electoral%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20respect%20to%20contributions%20through%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20the%20voter%20would%20not%20receive%20any%20information%20about%20financial%20contributions%20in%20terms%20of%20Section%2029C%20of%20RPA%20as%20amended%20by%20the%20Finance%20Act%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20(emphasis%20supplied)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20the%20minimum%20standard%20of%20transparency%20that%20the%20apex%20court%20adopted%20in%20the%20course%20of%20its%20theorisation%20of%20voters%E2%80%99%20right%20to%20know%20is%20%E2%80%9Ccomplete%20information%20about%20contributions%20made%20above%20twenty%20thousand%20%5BRs%2020%2C000%5D%20to%20a%20political%20party%E2%80%9D.%20This%20is%20not%20all.%20While%20striking%20down%20the%20amendment%20that%20was%20made%20to%20the%20Companies%20Act%2C%202013%20in%20order%20to%20facilitate%20anonymous%20donations%20to%20political%20parties%20by%20corporate%20entities%2C%20the%20court%20observed%20as%20follows%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20Court%20in%20the%20interim%20order%20dated%2031%20October%202023%20in%20the%20specific%20context%20of%20contributions%20made%20by%20companies%20through%20electoral%20bonds%20prima%20facie%20observed%20the%20voter%20would%20be%20able%20to%20secure%20information%20about%20the%20funding%20by%20matching%20the%20information%20of%20the%20aggregate%20sum%20contributed%20by%20the%20Company%20(as%20required%20to%20be%20disclosed%20under%20Section%20182(3)%20of%20the%20Companies%20Act%20as%20amended%20by%20the%20Finance%20Act)%20with%20the%20information%20disclosed%20by%20the%20political%20party.%20However%2C%20on%20a%20detailed%20analysis%20of%20the%20Scheme%20and%20the%20amendments%20we%20are%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%20such%20an%20exercise%20would%20not%20reveal%20the%20particulars%20of%20the%20donations%20because%20the%20Company%20under%20the%20provisions%20of%20Section%20182%20and%20the%20political%20party%20are%20only%20required%20to%20disclose%20the%20consolidated%20amount%20contributed%20and%20received%20through%20Electoral%20Bonds%20respectively.%20The%20particulars%20about%20the%20political%20party%20to%20which%20the%20contributions%20were%20made%20which%20is%20crucial%20to%20the%20right%20to%20information%20of%20political%20funding%20cannot%20be%20identified%20through%20the%20matching%20exercise%E2%80%A6.%E2%80%9D%20(emphasis%20supplied)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20above%20extract%20makes%20it%20abundantly%20clear%20that%20the%20court%20intended%20for%20voters%20to%20have%20complete%20information%20about%20contributions%2C%20enabling%20them%20to%20match%20donors%20with%20the%20political%20parties%20that%20receive%20donations%20from%20corporates.%20There%20is%20no%20indication%20in%20the%20theorization%20that%20the%20court%20intended%20otherwise%20for%20contributions%20made%20by%20individuals%20through%20EBs.%20However%2C%20the%20directives%20issued%20by%20the%20court%20at%20the%20end%20of%20its%20judgment%20fall%20woefully%20short%20of%20these%20two%20standards%20%E2%80%93%20namely%2C%20providing%20%E2%80%9Ccomplete%20information%20about%20contributions%20made%20above%20twenty%20thousand%20to%20a%20political%20party%E2%80%9D%20and%20enabling%20voters%2C%20through%20complete%20transparency%2C%20to%20%E2%80%9Cmatch%20the%20donor%20with%20the%20political%20party.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%E2%80%99s%20relevant%20directives%20for%20our%20discussion%20are%20reproduced%20below%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20view%20of%20our%20discussion%20above%2C%20the%20following%20directions%20are%20issued%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20issuing%20bank%20shall%20herewith%20stop%20the%20issuance%20of%20Electoral%20Bonds%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESBI%20shall%20submit%20details%20of%20the%20Electoral%20Bonds%20purchased%20since%20the%20interim%20order%20of%20this%20Court%20dated%2012%20April%202019%20till%20date%20to%20the%20ECI.%20The%20details%20shall%20include%20the%20date%20of%20purchase%20of%20each%20Electoral%20Bond%2C%20the%20name%20of%20the%20purchaser%20of%20the%20bond%20and%20the%20denomination%20of%20the%20Electoral%20Bond%20purchased%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESBI%20shall%20submit%20the%20details%20of%20political%20parties%20which%20have%20received%20contributions%20through%20Electoral%20Bonds%20since%20the%20interim%20order%20of%20this%20Court%20dated%2012%20April%202019%20till%20date%20to%20the%20ECI.%20SBI%20must%20disclose%20details%20of%20each%20Electoral%20Bond%20encashed%20by%20political%20parties%20which%20shall%20include%20the%20date%20of%20encashment%20and%20the%20denomination%20of%20the%20Electoral%20Bond%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESBI%20shall%20submit%20the%20above%20information%20to%20the%20ECI%20within%20three%20weeks%20from%20the%20date%20of%20this%20judgment%2C%20that%20is%2C%20by%206%20March%202024%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20ECI%20shall%20publish%20the%20information%20shared%20by%20the%20SBI%20on%20its%20official%20website%20within%20one%20week%20of%20the%20receipt%20of%20the%20information%2C%20that%20is%2C%20by%2013%20March%202024%3B%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20(emphasis%20supplied)%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20above%20directions%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20call%20for%20the%20disclosure%20of%20donor%20and%20recipient%20information%20separately%2C%20leaving%20voters%20with%20no%20mechanism%20to%20match%20the%20two%20categories%20of%20information.%20This%20omission%20prevents%20voters%20or%20the%20media%20from%20analysing%20and%20reporting%20on%20who%20paid%20how%20much%20to%20which%20political%20party%20through%20the%20EB%20route.%20It%20is%20respectfully%20submitted%20that%20this%20represents%20a%20shortcoming%20in%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20directives%20when%20compared%20with%20the%20standards%20it%20set%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Cvoters%E2%80%99%20right%20to%20know%E2%80%9D%20in%20its%20theorization%20of%20that%20principle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20other%20information%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20black-boxed%20by%20SBI%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENowhere%20in%20the%20February%202024%20judgment%20is%20there%20a%20listing%20or%20even%20a%20cursory%20mention%20of%20the%20kinds%20of%20information%20that%20SBI%20collected%20while%20selling%20EBs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EB%20Scheme%2C%20which%20the%20Union%20finance%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20Department%20of%20Economic%20Affairs%20notified%20in%20the%20official%20gazette%20contained%20only%20one%20proforma%2C%20namely%2C%20the%20application%20form%20which%20a%20prospective%20donor%20was%20required%20to%20fill%20up%20while%20buying%20EBs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20course%20of%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20EB%20Scheme%2C%20SBI%20collected%20much%20more%20information%20than%20the%20name%2C%20address%2C%20telephone%2Ffax%2Femail%20of%20the%20applicant.%20For%20example%2C%20in%20the%20case%20of%20individual%20donors%2C%20applicants%20were%20required%20to%20fill%20out%20a%20form%20that%20provided%20details%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9CControlling%20Person%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9CBeneficial%20Owner%E2%80%9D%20on%20whose%20behalf%20the%20EBs%20were%20being%20purchased%20from%20SBI.%20(see%20Images%201%20to%203%20below).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12111025%2FImage-11.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22849%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12111025%2FImage-11.jpg%20849w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12111025%2FImage-11-212x300.jpg%20212w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12111025%2FImage-11-724x1024.jpg%20724w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-701200%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EImage%201%3A%20Controlling%20Person%2FBeneficial%20Ownership%20Proforma%20issued%20by%20SBI%20for%20individual%20EB%20buyers%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20454px)%2085vw%2C%20454px%5C%22%20s