ntial%20status%2C%20occupation%20type%2C%20names%20of%20family%20members%20including%20mother%2C%20father%20and%20spouse%2C%20and%20tax%20residency%20status%20of%20the%20Controlling%20Person%20or%20Beneficial%20Owner%20on%20whose%20behalf%20the%20EBs%20were%20being%20purchased.%20A%20photograph%20of%20such%20person%20was%20also%20required%20to%20be%20affixed%20on%20this%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%20kind%20of%20anonymity%20did%20the%20government%20promise%20donors%20through%20the%20EB%20mechanism%20when%20SBI%20was%20collecting%20photographs%20of%20beneficial%20owners%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20SBI%20collected%20Beneficial%20Ownership%20details%20of%20the%20corporate%20entity%20on%20behalf%20of%20which%20EBs%20were%20bought%20by%20the%20applicant%20who%20signed%20the%20application%20form%20(see%20Images%204%20and%205%20below)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12111650%2FImage-4.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22849%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12111650%2FImage-4.jpg%20849w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12111650%2FImage-4-212x300.jpg%20212w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12111650%2FImage-4-724x1024.jpg%20724w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-701203%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EImage%204%3A%20Beneficial%20Ownership%20Proforma%20issued%20by%20SBI%20for%20corporate%20buyers%20of%20EBs%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12111928%2FImage-51.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22849%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12111928%2FImage-51.jpg%20849w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12111928%2FImage-51-212x300.jpg%20212w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12111928%2FImage-51-724x1024.jpg%20724w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-701204%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EImage%205%3A%20Beneficial%20Ownership%20Proforma%20issued%20by%20SBI%20for%20corporate%20buyers%20of%20EBs%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20these%20forms%20or%20categories%20of%20information%20that%20SBI%20planned%20to%20collect%20find%20a%20mention%20in%20the%20February%202024%20judgment.%20Did%20SBI%20collect%20all%20this%20information%3F%20This%20question%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20raised%20during%20the%20court%20proceedings.%20If%20SBI%20indeed%20collected%20all%20this%20information%2C%20it%20must%20be%20made%20public%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20standard%20of%20providing%20%E2%80%9Ccomplete%20information%E2%80%9D%20to%20enable%20the%20voter%20to%20make%20an%20informed%20choice%20at%20the%20polling%20booth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConclusion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuch%20like%20the%20EB-related%20FAQs%20which%20disappeared%20from%20SBI%E2%80%99s%20website%20as%20reported%20by%20the%20media%20recently%2C%20these%20proformas%20have%20also%20disappeared%20from%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20as%20I%20had%20downloaded%20them%20contemporaneously%20in%20order%20to%20file%20multiple%20RTI%20interventions%20(most%20of%20which%20failed%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20Central%20Information%20Commission%20decided%20the%20second%20appeals)%2C%20these%20forms%20can%20now%20be%20displayed%20publicly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20all%20these%20filled-up%20forms%20are%20black-boxed.%20We%20do%20not%20know%20how%20soon%20SBI%20might%20destroy%20them.%20If%20hundreds%20of%20citizens%20were%20to%20file%20RTI%20applications%20seeking%20this%20information%20from%20every%20SBI%20branch%20that%20sold%20EBs%2C%20there%20is%20a%20good%20chance%20they%20might%20be%20preserved%20because%20destroying%20information%20that%20is%20subject%20of%20a%20pending%20RTI%20application%20attracts%20a%20penalty%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%2025%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20plan%20to%20file%20my%20RTIs%20soon%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20you%20want%20to%20do%20so%2C%20as%20well%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EVenkatesh%20Nayak%20is%20director%2C%20Commonwealth%20Human%20Rights%20Initiative%2C%20New%20Delhi.%20All%20facts%20are%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20Views%20are%20personal.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710235814000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F05105750%2F1166496076_ac2efae08c_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fafter-faqs-on-electoral-bonds-sbis-beneficial-ownership-proformas-disappear-from-website%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20proformas%20are%20those%20that%20require%20details%20of%20who%20is%20buying%20the%20bonds.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fafter-faqs-on-electoral-bonds-sbis-beneficial-ownership-proformas-disappear-from-website%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThink%20Before%20You%20Apply%26quot%3B%3A%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20Citizenship%20Law%20Warning%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHitting%20out%20at%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20over%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%2C%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20%26quot%3Btrying%20to%20create%20unrest%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20yesterday's%20announcement%20is%20a%20%26quot%3BLudo%20move%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20an%20administrative%20meeting%20at%20Bengal's%20Habra%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20chief%20alleged%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20%26quot%3Bsnatch%20away%20citizenship%20rights%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20she%20doubts%20the%20legality%20of%20the%20law.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20clarity.%20It%20is%20a%20misleading%20campaign%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBJP%20leaders%20say%20CAA%20gives%20you%20rights.%20But%20the%20moment%20you%20apply%20for%20citizenship%2C%20you%20become%20illegal%20migrants%20and%20you%20will%20lose%20your%20rights.%20You%20will%20lose%20rights%20and%20be%20taken%20to%20detention%20camps.%20Please%20think%20before%20you%20apply%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20will%20happen%20to%20the%20assets%20of%20those%20people%20who%20don't%20get%20citizenship%3F%20This%20is%20BJP's%20game%20of%20Ludo%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee%20said%20the%20CAA's%20implementation%20will%20be%20followed%20by%20work%20on%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20(NRC).%20The%20NRC%20is%20a%20record%20of%20Indian%20citizens%20that%20has%20been%20implemented%20only%20in%20Assam%20so%20far.%20In%202019%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20had%20said%20that%20a%20pan-India%20NRC%20was%20not%20on%20the%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRemember%2C%20CAA%20is%20linked%20to%20NRC.%20People%20will%20be%20taken%20to%20detention%20camps.%20I%20will%20not%20allow%20this%20to%20happen%20in%20Bengal.%20Have%20you%20ever%20heard%20of%20citizenship%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20religion%3F%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Banerjee%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20chief%20described%20the%20new%20law%20as%20%26quot%3Banother%20game%20to%20divide%20Bengal%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20not%20let%20this%20happen.%20We%20are%20all%20citizens%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20last%20evening%20issued%20a%20notification%20for%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%2C%20under%20which%20non-Muslim%20migrants%20from%20Bangladesh%2C%20Pakistan%20and%20Afghanistan%20fleeing%20religious%20persecution%20can%20seek%20Indian%20citizenship.%20Persons%20from%20Hindu%2C%20Sikh%2C%20Buddhist%2C%20Jain%2C%20Parsi%20or%20Christian%20communities%20from%20these%20countries%2C%20who%20entered%20India%20on%20or%20before%20December%2031%2C%202014%2C%20can%20seek%20citizenship%20under%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20parties%20have%20criticised%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Act%2C%20which%20cleared%20the%20Parliament%20in%202019.%20They%20have%20pointed%20to%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20with%20the%20main%20Opposition%20Congress%20alleging%20a%20polarisation%20plan%20by%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Trinamool%2C%20however%2C%20yesterday's%20announcement%20poses%20a%20bigger%20poll%20challenge.%20Implementation%20of%20CAA%20was%20a%20longstanding%20demand%20of%20Matuas%2C%20a%20Hindu%20scheduled%20caste%20group%20with%20roots%20in%20present-day%20Bangladesh.%20Most%20members%20of%20the%20community%20had%20entered%20Bengal%20after%20Partition%20or%20after%20Bangladesh%20was%20formed.%20The%20group%20is%20politically%20significant%2C%20and%20both%20the%20BJP%20and%20Trinamool%20have%20left%20no%20stone%20unturned%20to%20woo%20Matuas%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20state%20and%20national%20elections.%20The%20BJP%20now%20hopes%20that%20yesterday's%20announcement%20may%20tilt%20the%20scales%20in%20its%20favour.%20Following%20the%20announcement%20last%20evening%2C%20celebrations%20were%20held%20in%20areas%20dominated%20by%20the%20Matua%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocal%20BJP%20MP%20and%20Union%20Minister%20Shantanu%20Thakur%20thanked%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20for%20fulfilling%20the%20dream%20of%20three%20generations%20of%20Matuas%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20section%20of%20the%20community%2C%20which%20supports%20the%20Trinamool%2C%20was%20sceptical.%20Mamatabala%20Thakur%2C%20a%20former%20MP%20from%20the%20party%2C%20said%20the%20Centre's%20announcement%20is%20aimed%20at%20getting%20votes.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20about%20the%20citizenship%20rights%20already%20granted%20to%20Matuas%20after%201947%3F%20Will%20the%20CAA%20force%20them%20to%20come%20up%20with%20identity%20proofs%20once%20again%20and%20throw%20them%20into%20an%20uncertain%20future%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApparently%20referring%20to%20the%20seats%20dominated%20by%20the%20Matua%20community%2C%20Ms%20Banerjee%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAll%20of%20this%20just%20to%20win%201%20or%202%20seats%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWill%20you%20hand%20over%20your%20future%20to%20the%20BJP%20for%20an%20election%3F%20This%20is%20to%20harass%20people%20and%20win%20seats.%20My%20Matua%20brothers%20and%20sisters%2C%20do%20you%20believe%20in%20this%3F%20Will%20you%20be%20able%20to%20vote%3F%20Don't%20walk%20this%20path.%20BJP%20will%20say%20many%20things%2C%20but%20it%20is%20a%20lie%20and%20a%20jumla%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710235800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fqm3qh9ng_mamata-banerjee_625x300_10_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmamata-banerjees-ludo-barb-at-bjp-over-citizenship-law-and-nrc-warning-5223787%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hitting%20out%20at%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20over%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%2C%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20%26quot%3Btrying%20to%20create%20unrest%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20yesterday's%20announcement%20is%20a%20%26quot%3BLudo%20move%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmamata-banerjees-ludo-barb-at-bjp-over-citizenship-law-and-n