seat-sharing%20talks%20with%20its%20allies%20in%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%2C%20even%20as%20its%20leaders%20have%20attempted%20to%20amplify%20similar%20hurdles%20in%20the%20opposition%20camp%20as%20a%20sure%20sign%20of%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA)%E2%80%99s%20failure%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20saffron%20party%E2%80%99s%20latest%20struggle%20with%20allies%20is%20best%20reflected%20in%20the%20way%20the%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar-led%20Haryana%20government%20resigned%20with%20his%20cabinet%20on%20Tuesday%20morning%2C%20hours%20after%20the%20BJP%20and%20Jannayak%20Janta%20Party%20(JJP)%20led%20by%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Dushyant%20Chautala%20collapsed.%20It%20is%20said%20that%20the%20JJP%20insisted%20on%20contesting%20two%20seats%2C%20including%20the%20prestigious%20Rohtak%2C%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20but%20the%20BJP%20didn%E2%80%99t%20relent.%20As%20their%20alliance%20headed%20for%20a%20split%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20now%20tried%20to%20checkmate%20its%20own%20ally%20%E2%80%93%20with%20a%20plan%20that%20it%20would%20still%20helm%20the%20state%20government%20by%20cobbling%20up%20a%20majority%20with%20the%20help%20of%20independents.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20unpopular%20chief%20minister%20Khattar%2C%20too%2C%20resigning%2C%20the%20BJP%20hopes%20to%20repeat%20the%20Gujarat%20experiment%20where%20Vijay%20Rupani%20was%20replaced%20with%20Bhupendra%20Patel%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20months%20ahead%20of%20the%20state%20assembly%20polls%20in%202022%2C%20giving%20enough%20to%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20media%20machinery%20to%20spin%20its%20political%20crisis%20as%20course%20correction.%20However%2C%20each%20time%20the%20BJP%20faces%20such%20a%20crisis%2C%20it%20has%20taken%20it%20as%20a%20window%20of%20opportunity%20to%20assert%20its%20weight%20against%20its%20own%20allies%2C%20forgetting%20the%20principles%20of%20alliance%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edharma%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ethat%20the%20prime%20minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20often%20cites%20in%20his%20speeches.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBetween%20BJP%20bombast%20and%20truth%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhatever%20ways%20in%20which%20the%20BJP%20spins%20a%20positive%20narrative%20out%20of%20its%20crisis%2C%20the%20very%20nature%20of%20coalition%20politics%20of%20India%20has%20always%20pulled%20it%20backwards%20from%20its%20overt%20propensity%20to%20become%20a%20hegemonic%20force.%20The%20Haryana%20episode%20has%20once%20again%20proven%20that%20the%20BJP%2C%20like%20all%20other%20political%20parties%20in%20the%20opposition%2C%20has%20tricky%20issues%20to%20deal%20with%20before%20it%20enters%20the%20electoral%20fray%20%E2%80%93%20and%20none%20of%20those%20alone%20decides%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20elections.%20The%20saffron%20party%E2%80%99s%20contention%20that%20the%20ups%20and%20downs%20in%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20over%20seat-sharing%20issues%20is%20an%20admission%20of%20defeat%2C%20or%20shows%20how%20%E2%80%9Cunprincipled%E2%80%9D%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20is%2C%20smacks%20of%20nothing%20but%20propaganda.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHad%20the%20BJP%20been%20in%20such%20a%20great%20position%20to%20secure%20its%20%E2%80%9CMission%20370%E2%80%9D%20goal%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20it%20need%20not%20have%20entered%20into%20an%20alliance%20with%20rivals%20like%20the%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20in%20Odisha%20and%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20For%20years%20now%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20critiqued%20and%20opposed%20the%20Naveen%20Patnaik%20government%20in%20Odisha%2C%20and%20had%20in%20fact%20carved%20out%20a%20substantive%20opposition%20space%20for%20itself%20in%20the%20eastern%20state.%20But%20burying%20all%20electoral%20aspirations%20of%20its%20state%20leaders%2C%20the%20Modi-Shah%20duo%20has%20now%20decided%20to%20form%20a%20pre-poll%20coalition%20with%20its%20arch-rival%20in%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFriends%2C%20foes%2C%20friends%20again%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20ever%20since%20TDP%20chief%20N.%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20exited%20the%20NDA%20following%20an%20acrimonious%20break-up%20in%202018%2C%20the%20BJP%20leaders%20left%20no%20opportunity%20to%20lash%20out%20at%20the%20Andhra%20leader.%20They%20called%20him%20corrupt%2C%20immoral%2C%20opportunistic%2C%20and%20even%20helped%20the%20YSR%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20government%20in%20the%20state%20to%20get%20him%20arrested%20over%20corruption%20charges%20that%20at%20one%20point%20the%20Modi-led%20Centre%20was%20pursuing.%20However%2C%20as%20things%20stand%20today%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20chosen%20Naidu%20over%20Reddy%20as%20an%20ally%2C%20and%20is%20all%20set%20to%20fight%20both%20the%20assembly%20and%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20together.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20BJP%20didn%E2%80%99t%20hesitate%20for%20once%20in%20joining%20ranks%20with%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20against%20whom%20it%20had%20led%20a%20toxic%20campaign%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years.%20Nitish%20Kumar%20played%20the%20most%20instrumental%20role%20in%20creating%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%20Over%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20the%20BJP%20attempted%20to%20create%20multiple%20situations%20to%20break%20his%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20and%20topple%20his%20government%20that%20it%20often%20accused%20of%20promoting%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ejungleraaj%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D.%20But%20when%20it%20came%20to%20reuniting%20with%20Kumar%2C%20the%20BJP%20didn%E2%80%99t%20think%20twice.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20should%20be%20credited%20for%20forging%20new%20partnerships%20better%20than%20most%20opposition%20parties.%20But%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20respecting%20its%20allies%2C%20it%20is%20worse%20than%20most.%20Think%20of%20how%20it%20treated%20its%20smaller%20OBC%20allies%20like%20Om%20Prakash%20Rajbhar%20or%20Swami%20Prasad%20Maurya%20soon%20after%20the%20BJP%20registered%20a%20comprehensive%20victory%20in%20the%202017%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20assembly%20polls.%20Now%2C%20as%20yet%20another%20round%20of%20elections%20are%20here%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20already%20roped%20in%20Rajbhar%20and%20is%20looking%20to%20collaborate%20with%20Maurya.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilar%20big-brotherly%20attitude%20has%20cost%20the%20BJP%20all%20its%20big%20allies%20like%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20Shiromani%20Akali%20Dal%20(Badal)%2C%20and%2C%20at%20one%20point%2C%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(United).%20Yet%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20run%20roughshod%20over%20them%20by%20using%20blunt%20force%2C%20allegedly%20misusing%20central%20investigation%20agencies%20against%20leaders%2C%20attempting%20to%20split%20the%20parties%2C%20and%20believing%20that%20its%20unparalleled%20money%20and%20muscle%20power%20can%20overcome%20all%20its%20political%20crises.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESmall%20parties%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20partners%20but%20not%20allies%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20nothing%20ideological%20and%20principled%20about%20the%20Modi-led%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20operations.%20The%20JJP%20and%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20split%20offers%20a%20classic%20case-study%20for%20how%20the%20BJP%20has%20chosen%20to%20conduct%20business%20with%20smaller%2C%20but%20very%20important%20players%20in%20key%20states.%20One%20also%20hears%20that%20the%20seat-sharing%20talks%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20allies%20in%20Maharashtra%20are%20stuck.%20Its%20Maharashtra%20allies%2C%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde%20faction%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%2C%20are%20the%20starkest%20examples%20of%20the%20Modi-Shah%20duo%E2%80%99s%20Machiavellian%20games.%20The%20BJP%20has%20reportedly%20taken%20a%20lion%E2%80%99s%20share%20of%2030-32%2C%20while%20handing%20around%2011-12%20seats%20to%20Shinde%20and%204-5%20seats%20to%20Ajit%20Pawar.%20However%2C%20the%20disagreements%20over%20six%20seats%20has%20made%20the%20equations%20bitter%20between%20the%20three%20parties.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20may%20be%20adept%20at%20enticing%20partners%2C%20possibly%20because%20of%20its%20huge%20resources%2C%20but%20have%20also%20shown%20hostility%20towards%20their%20independent%20demands.%20This%20has%20resulted%20in%20bitter%20breakups%2C%20often%20following%20episodes%20where%20the%20BJP%20has%20tried%20to%20sabotage%20its%20own%20ally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20saffron%20party%20may%20be%20good%20at%20managing%20news%20headlines%2C%20but%20it%20is%20certainly%20not%20free%20from%20the%20pulls%20and%20pressures%20of%20realpolitik%2C%20as%20much%20as%20it%20would%20want%20to%20project%20itself%20as%20different%20from%20others.%20%3Cspan%3EThe%20run-up%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20has%20shown%20once%20again%20the%20messy%20nature%20of%20electoral%20play%2C%20which%20can%20sometimes%20be%20a%20positive%20trend%20for%20Indian%20democracy%2C%20as%20it%20allows%20a%20play%20for%20diversity%20in%20its%20politics.%20If%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20appears%20to%20be%20struggling%20to%20bring%20opposition%20forces%20together%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20too%2C%20is%20wrestling%20to%20save%20the%20NDA%20from%20any%20further%20embarrassment%2C%20especially%20after%20it%20got%20a%20tight%20rap%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20case.%20A%20tough%20electoral%20race%20ahead%20is%20surely%20in%20the%20offing%2C%20despite%20what%20the%20BJP%20would%20like%20us%20to%20think.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710235385000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2FModi-Shah.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-hobbled-by-nda-trouble-and-struggle-in-key-states%22%2