-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Haryana%3A%20BJP%20Picks%20State%20Chief%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini%20as%20New%20CM%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12142049%2Fimage-1933.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChandigarh%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20a%20significant%20political%20development%2C%20Haryana%20chief%20minister%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%2C%20along%20with%20his%20cabinet%2C%20resigned%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20March%2012%2C%20as%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20initiated%20the%20process%20for%20forming%20a%20new%20government%20in%20collaboration%20with%20independent%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20expected%20to%20announce%20Khattar%E2%80%99s%20replacement%20soon%20after%20its%20legislative%20party%20meeting%2C%20which%20has%20commenced%20at%20Haryana%20Niwas%20in%20Sector%203%20of%20Chandigarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20central%20party%20observers%20%E2%80%93%20Union%20minister%20Arjun%20Munda%20and%20BJP%20National%20General%20Secretary%20Tarun%20Chugh%20%E2%80%93%20have%20already%20arrived%20to%20oversee%20the%20smooth%20transition%20of%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20official%20word%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20out%2C%20the%20immediate%20trigger%20appears%20to%20be%20the%20collapse%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20four-and-a-half-year%20alliance%20with%20the%20Jannayak%20Janata%20Party%20(JJP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJJP%2C%20which%20emerged%20from%20a%20split%20in%20the%20Chautala%20family%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Lok%20Dal%2C%20fought%20the%20last%20assembly%20election%20against%20the%20BJP%20but%20later%20came%20on%20board%20to%20form%20an%20alliance%20after%20the%20latter%20fell%20short%20of%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20differences%20in%20seat%20allotment%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20are%20believed%20to%20be%20the%20core%20reason%20for%20the%20rift%20in%20the%20BJP-JJP%20alliance%2C%20which%20has%20been%20under%20strain%20for%20the%20past%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20sources%20indicate%20that%20the%20BJP%20Haryana%20cadre%20was%20also%20discontent%20with%20the%20alliance%20with%20the%20JJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20believe%20that%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20recent%20decision%20to%20split%20from%20the%20JJP%20and%20form%20a%20new%20government%20was%20done%20to%20counter%20anti-incumbency%20in%20the%20upcoming%20general%20elections.%20The%20move%20was%20also%20aimed%20at%20splitting%20the%20dominant%20jat%20votes%20by%20leaving%20the%20JJP%20on%20its%20own%20and%20let%20it%20compete%20with%20the%20Congress%20for%20jat%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20BJP%20won%20all%2010%20parliamentary%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%20But%20it%20remains%20a%20challenge%20for%20the%20party%20to%20repeat%20its%20last%20election%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENote%20that%20immediately%20after%20the%20general%20election%2C%20Haryana%20will%20hold%20assembly%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20possible%20change%20in%20leadership%2C%20BJP%20will%20also%20try%20to%20neutralise%20the%20growing%20unpopularity%20against%20Khattar%2C%20who%20has%20been%20chief%20minister%20for%20the%20last%20nine-and-a-half%20years%2C%20and%20hope%20that%20a%20Gujarat-like%20move%20will%20help%20them%20stay%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20learnt%20that%20the%20BJP%20also%20changed%20government%20months%20before%20the%20Gujarat%20assembly%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndependents%20extend%20support%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%2C%20which%20currently%20has%2041%20MLAs%20in%20the%2090-member%20state%20assembly%2C%20needs%20support%20of%20five%20more%20MLAs%20to%20remain%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20all%20five%20independent%20MLAs%20have%20already%20extended%20support%20to%20the%20BJP.%20Besides%2C%20Sirsa%20MLA%20and%20President-Haryana%20Lokhit%20Party%2C%20Gopal%20Kanda%2C%20too%2C%20extended%20support%20to%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanda%2C%20in%20a%20media%20statement%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20think%20the%20alliance%20(BJP-JJP)%20has%20almost%20broken.%20Even%20without%20the%20JJP%2C%20the%20Haryana%20government%20will%20stay%2C%20and%20all%20independent%20candidates%20will%20continue%20to%20support%20the%20BJP.%20%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20that%20many%20of%20these%20independents%20may%20be%20rewarded%20with%20a%20cabinet%20berth%20in%20the%20new%20BJP%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20BJP%20leader%20Kanwar%20Pal%20Gujjar%20confirmed%20that%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20cabinet%20ministers%20have%20resigned%2C%20and%20the%20governor%20has%20accepted%20the%20resignations.%20The%20next%20move%20will%20be%20determined%20after%20the%20legislative%20party%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710233142000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F14121527%2FF3T6TBIb0AAY7VK.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fharyana-cm-manohar-lal-khattar-resigns-amid-rift-between-bjp-jjp-alliance-over-seat-sharing%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%2C%20along%20with%20his%20cabinet%2C%20resigned%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20March%2012%2C%20as%20the%20BJP%20initiated%20the%20process%20for%20forming%20a%20new%20government%20in%20collaboration%20with%20independent%20candidates.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fharyana-cm-manohar-lal-khattar-resigns-amid-rift-between-bjp-jjp-alliance-over-seat-sharing%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SRK's%20film%20with%20Suhana%20is%20back%20on%20track%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710233059000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108429834%2Cimgsize-27550.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fshah-rukh-khans-film-with-daughter-suhana-back-on-track-deets-inside%2Farticleshow%2F108429840.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108429840.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EDirector%20Sujoy%20Ghosh%20is%20working%20on%20a%20project%20with%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20and%20his%20daughter%20Suhana%20Khan.%20The%20film%20draws%20inspiration%20from%20Rabindranath%20Tagore's%20'Kabuliwala'%20and%20Luc%20Besson's%20'Leon%3A%20The%20Professional.'%20It%20features%20a%20narrative%20about%20a%20solitary%20individual%20entangled%20in%20issues%20with%20anti-social%20elements.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fshah-rukh-khans-film-with-daughter-suhana-back-on-track-deets-inside%2Farticleshow%2F108429840.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Giant%20Mysterious%20Monolith%20Spotted%20On%20Remote%20UK%20Hill%2C%20Sparks%20Speculation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20gigantic%20steel%20monolith%20was%20recently%20spotted%20on%20a%20hill%20in%20Wales%2C%20baffling%20locals%20and%20experts%20alike.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F03%2F11%2Flifestyle%2F10-foot-mysterious-metal-monolith-appears-on-remote-uk-hill%2F%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Post%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%2010-foot-tall%20block%20of%20steel%2C%20which%20is%20shaped%20like%20a%20giant%20Toblerone%2C%20was%20spotted%20by%20locals%C2%A0on%20Hay%20Bluff%20near%20the%20Powys%20town%20at%20the%20weekend.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''I%20thought%20it%20looked%20a%20bit%20bizarre%20and%20might%20be%20a%20scientific%20media%20research%20thing%20collecting%20rainwater%2C%E2%80%9D%20Richard%20Haynes%20told%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walesonline.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fwales-news%2Fgiant-monolith-appears-top-welsh-28795875%5C%22%3EWales%20Online%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20then%20realized%20it%20was%20way%20too%20tall%20and%20strange%20for%20that.%20Then%20I%20went%20up%20to%20it%20and%20it%20was%20about%2010-foot-tall%20at%20least%20and%20triangular%2C%20definitely%20stainless%20steel.%20It%20was%20hollow%20and%20I%20imagine%20pretty%20light.%20Light%20enough%20for%20two%20people%20to%20carry%20it%20up%20and%20plant%20it%20in%20the%20ground%2C''%20Mr%20Haynes%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pictures%20of%20the%20monolith%20that%20have%20gone%20viral%2C%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNickHintonn%2Fstatus%2F1767454707033739741%2Fphoto%2F1%5C%22%3Eevoked%20several%20conspiracy%20theories%3C%2Fa%3E%20online.%20While%20many%20said%20it%20was%20the%20work%20of%20aliens%2C%20others%20were%20convinced%20that%20it%20was%20an%20elaborate%20piece%20of%20undercover%20artwork.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20this%20unusual%20sighting%2C%20a%20string%20of%20monoliths%20has%20appeared%20across%20the%20world%2C%C2%A0becoming%20the%20subject%20of%20intense%20public%20curiosity%20and%20speculation.%C2%A0Theories%20about%20their%20origins%20ranged%20from%20a%20marketing%20ploy%20to%20extraterrestrials.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202021%2C%20a%20mysterious%2010-foot-tall%20metal%20slab%20appeared%20in%20southeastern%20Turkey%2C%20then%20quietly%20disappeared%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2021%2F02%2F10%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fturkey-monolith.html%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E.%20It%20was%20inscribed%20with%20a%20cryptic%20message%20in%20the%20Gokturk%20alphabet%2C%20an%20ancient%20Turkic%20language%2C%20''Look%20at%20the%20sky%2C%20see%20the%20moon.''%20It%20later%C2%A0turned%20ou