-on-jackky-bhagnanis-first-meeting-with-her-father-i-was-nervous%2Farticleshow%2F108428995.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tension%20Between%20Israel%20And%20US%20Is%20Rising%20With%20Gaza%20Death%20Count%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20almost-daily%20phone%20calls%20stopped%20months%20ago.%20Now%20the%20tensions%20between%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20over%20Israel's%20war%20on%20Hamas%20have%20burst%20into%20the%20open%20as%20the%20two%20leaders%20bicker%20publicly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELate%20last%20week%2C%20the%20US%20announced%20its%20army%20would%20build%20a%20pier%20to%20bring%20aid%20to%20civilians%20in%20Gaza%2C%20with%20food%20short%20and%20relief%20groups%20warning%20of%20famine%20amid%20Israel's%20assault.%20Biden%20demanded%20the%20Israeli%20leader%20%26quot%3Bpay%20more%20attention%20to%20the%20innocent%20lives%20being%20lost%2C%26quot%3B%20warning%20that%20%26quot%3Bhe%20is%20hurting%20Israel%20more%20than%20helping%20Israel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%20fired%20back%20the%20next%20day.%20%26quot%3BHe's%20wrong%20on%20both%20counts%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Politico%20parent%20Axel%20Springer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20public%20back-and-forth%20was%20a%20dramatic%20departure%20from%20Biden's%20public%20embrace%20of%20Israel%20after%20the%20October%207%20Hamas%20attacks%2C%20the%20deadliest%20in%20the%20country's%20history.%20The%20US%20president%20worked%20closely%20with%20Netanyahu%20to%20deliver%20sweeping%20military%20and%20diplomatic%20support.%20But%20with%20more%20than%2030%2C000%20dead%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Hamas-run%20Gaza%20health%20ministry%2C%20and%20Israel%20planning%20an%20assault%20on%20Rafah%2C%20the%20last%20major%20city%20in%20the%20enclave%20where%20residents%20are%20sheltering%2C%20tensions%20between%20the%20Israeli%20leader%20and%20his%20most%20important%20ally%20over%20the%20civilian%20death%20toll%20have%20become%20impossible%20to%20conceal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20was%20caught%20on%20a%20hot%20mic%20Thursday%20telling%20a%20legislator%20that%20he%20planned%20a%20%26quot%3Bcome-to-Jesus%26quot%3B%20meeting%20with%20Netanyahu.%20That%20came%20just%20days%20after%20his%20administration%20hosted%20Benny%20Gantz%2C%20a%20member%20of%20Israel's%20war%20cabinet%20but%20also%20Netanyahu's%20main%20political%20rival%2C%20for%20top-level%20meetings%20in%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20leader%20smelled%20betrayal.%20%26quot%3BTo%20the%20extent%20that%20Hamas%20believes%20that%20there's%20daylight%20between%20us%2C%20that%20doesn't%20help%2C%26quot%3B%20Netanyahu%20told%20Fox%20News%20Monday.%20Hamas%20has%20been%20designated%20a%20terrorist%20organization%20by%20the%20US%20and%20European%20Union.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20moment%2C%20the%20Biden%20administration%20has%20kept%20up%20the%20flow%20of%20weapons%20and%20other%20support%20to%20Israel%2C%20even%20as%20it%20steps%20in%20to%20deliver%20humanitarian%20aid%20directly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%2C%2081%2C%20and%20Netanyahu%2C%2074%2C%20have%20differed%20for%20decades.%20But%20this%20time%2C%20the%20tensions%20are%20even%20more%20real.%20The%20US%20argues%20Israel%20isn't%20doing%20enough%20to%20limit%20death%20and%20suffering%20among%20the%20millions%20of%20ordinary%20Palestinians%20who%20have%20no%20link%20to%20Hamas%20and%20its%20violent%20policies.%20In%20northern%20Gaza%2C%20US%20officials%20note%2C%20citing%20a%20World%20Heath%20Organization%20statement%2C%20a%20dozen%20children%20have%20starved%20to%20death%20while%20their%20parents%20eat%20grass%20and%20use%20animal%20feed%20for%20flour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden's%20under%20increasing%20pressure%20to%20do%20more%20to%20rein%20in%20his%20ally%2C%20both%20from%20other%20capitals%20and%20from%20key%20supporters%20at%20home%2C%20where%20liberal%20and%20younger%20voters%20are%20demanding%20an%20end%20to%20support%20for%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20two%20people%20who%20are%20exquisitely%20skilled%20and%20exquisitely%20sensitive%20politicians%2C%20who%2C%20rather%20than%20trying%20to%20help%20each%20other%2C%20are%20trying%20to%20squeeze%20each%20other%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jon%20Alterman%2C%20director%20of%20the%20Middle%20East%20program%20at%20the%20Center%20for%20Strategic%20and%20International%20Studies%20in%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deaths%20of%20some%20100%20Gazans%20seeking%20aid%20from%20a%20convoy%20at%20the%20end%20of%20February%20became%20a%20turning%20point%2C%20US%20officials%20said.%20That%20event%20involved%20some%20shooting%20by%20Israeli%20troops%20but%20mostly%2C%20Israel%20says%2C%20trampling%20due%20to%20a%20stampede.%20It%20rejects%20the%20idea%20that%20it's%20been%20careless%20toward%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20close%20to%20Netanyahu%20argue%20that%20US%20policy%20is%20now%20aimed%20at%20separating%20the%20prime%20minister%20from%20his%20electorate%20in%20the%20hope%20of%20causing%20a%20political%20crisis%20in%20Israel%20that%20will%20lead%20to%20a%20more%20moderate%20government%20without%20Netanyahu%20and%20his%20far-right%20coalition%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20evident%20when%20Biden%20sanctioned%20extremist%20Jewish%20West%20Bank%20settlers%2C%20the%20key%20constituents%20of%20Netanyahu's%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20report%20to%20Congress%20Monday%2C%20the%20US%20intelligence%20community%20questioned%20%26quot%3BNetanyahu's%20viability%20as%20leader.%26quot%3B%20It%20predicted%20%26quot%3Blarge%20protests%20demanding%20his%20resignation%20and%20new%20elections%26quot%3B%20that%20it%20said%20may%20lead%20to%20a%20more%20moderate%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20likely%20that%20the%20Gaza%20conflict%20will%20have%20a%20generational%20impact%20on%20terrorism%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%2C%20underscoring%20US%20intelligence%20agencies'%20concerns%20about%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20devastation%20in%20the%20Palestinian%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20his%20part%2C%20Netanyahu%2C%20the%20country's%20longest-serving%20prime%20minister%2C%20made%20sure%20in%20his%20Sunday%20interview%20to%20argue%20that%20he's%20not%20leading%20his%20nation%20anywhere%20it%20doesn't%20wish%20to%20go.%20A%20recent%20poll%20by%20the%20Israel%20Democracy%20Institute%20found%2075%25%20of%20Jewish%20Israelis%20favor%20expanding%20military%20operations%20in%20Rafah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhite%20House%20spokeswoman%20Olivia%20Dalton%20said%20Monday%20that%20Biden's%20decades-long%20ties%20with%20the%20Israeli%20leader%20allow%20the%20US%20president%20%26quot%3Bto%20be%20direct%20and%20honest%20at%20a%20time%20where%20that's%20needed.%20But%20there's%20no%20change%20here%20in%20the%20strength%20of%20the%20two%20leaders'%20relationship.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%20says%20Israel%20will%20eventually%20invade%20Rafah%2C%20the%20southern%20Gaza%20city%2C%20where%20some%208%2C000%20Hamas%20fighters%2C%20its%20leaders%20and%20the%20remaining%20134%20Israeli%20hostages%20are%20thought%20to%20be%20ensconced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20doesn't%20want%20Israel%20to%20move%20forward%20out%20of%20fear%20that%20too%20many%20civilians%20will%20be%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20view%20is%20that%20no%20military%20operation%20should%20take%20place%20in%20Rafah%20if%20there%20is%20not%20a%20credible%20and%20implementable%20plan%20to%20take%20care%20of%20the%20safety%20and%20security%20needs%20of%20the%20more%20than%20a%20million%20civilians%20who%20are%20sheltering%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Dalton%2C%20the%20White%20House%20spokeswoman%2C%20said%20Monday.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20we've%20seen%20no%20such%20plan.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Forces%20Are%20Preparing%20a%20Push%20Into%20Rafah%20%7C%20More%20than%20one%20million%20people%20have%20sought%20refuge%20in%20the%20south%20Gaza%20city%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20Gantz%2C%20a%20popular%20opposition%20politician%2C%20met%20officials%20in%20Washington%20last%20week%2C%20his%20message%20was%20clear%3A%20The%20attack%20on%20Rafah%20must%20proceed%20eventually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tensions%20extend%20beyond%20the%20current%20fighting.%20The%20Biden%20administration%20believes%20that%20it's%20time%20to%20start%20planning%20for%20the%20day%20after%20the%20war%2C%20meaning%20a%20regional%20arrangement%20involving%20Saudi%20and%20Emirati%20aid%20for%20a%20Palestinian%20state%20to%20run%20Gaza%20and%20the%20West%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20anathema%20to%20Netanyahu%20who%20says%20if%20a%20Palestinian%20state%20is%20the%20result%20of%20the%20October%207%20massacre%2C%20that%20rewards%20terror.%20Palestinians%2C%20he%20and%20his%20aides%20say%2C%20must%20learn%20the%20opposite%20-%20that%20violence%20will%20bring%20only%20harsh%20reprisal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20say%20something%20else%3A%20The%20more%20Biden%20tries%20to%20drive%20a%20wedge%20between%20the%20Israeli%20public%20and%20their%20prime%20minister%2C%20the%20stronger%20he%20will%20make%20Netanyahu%20because%20voters%20don't%20appreciate%20such%20interference.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710231360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F42v9reng_joe-biden-netanyahu-reuters_650x400_18_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftension-between-israel-and-us-is-rising-with-gaza-death-count-5223643%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20almost-daily%20phone%20calls%20stopped%20months%20ago.%20Now%20the%20tensions%20between%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20over%20Israel's%20war%20on%20Hamas%20have%20burst%20into%20the%20open%20as%20the%20two%20leaders%20bicker%20publicly.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftension-between-israel-and-us-is-rising-with-gaza-death-count-5223643%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.