o%20another%20location%20identified%20by%20the%20state%20government.%20One%20local%20resident%20was%20injured%20in%20the%20blast.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20arrested%20two%20persons%20based%20on%20strong%20evidence%20of%20their%20involvement%20in%20the%20IED%20blast%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rituraj%20Ravi%2C%20the%20district%20police%20chief%20of%20the%20East%20Khasi%20Hills%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.co.in%2Furl%3Fsa%3Dt%26rct%3Dj%26q%3D%26esrc%3Ds%26source%3Dweb%26cd%3D%26cad%3Drja%26uact%3D8%26ved%3D2ahUKEwip-MKRie6EAxX9cGwGHcxYDmAQvOMEKAB6BAgSEAE%26url%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fwww.uniindia.com%252Ftwo-persons-arrested-in-connection-with-ied-blast-in-meghalaya%252Feast%252Fnews%252F3159634.html%26usg%3DAOvVaw2WFmMIVohESMNKP63Y2Ywz%26opi%3D89978449%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20United%20News%20of%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20arrests%20were%20carried%20out%20on%20March%2010.%20While%20one%20of%20them%20has%20been%20identified%20as%2026-year-old%20Ebakorda%20Nongpluh%2C%20arrested%20from%20Shillong%2C%20the%20other%20person%20is%2058-year-old%20Tarson%20Lymba%2C%20currently%20the%20disciplinary%20secretary%20of%20Hynniewtrep%20National%20Youth%20Front%20(HNYF)%2C%20picked%20from%20Dawki%20close%20to%20the%20India-Bangladesh%20border.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELymba%20was%20also%20the%20interlocutor%20for%20the%20peace%20talks%20that%20the%20state%20government%20had%20begun%20with%20the%20banned%20armed%20outfit%2C%20the%20Hynniewtrep%20National%20Liberation%20Council%20(HNLC).%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20HNLA%2C%20however%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fmeghalaya-extremist-group-withdraws-from-talks%2Farticle67702876.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Hynniewtrep%2520National%2520Liberation%2520Council%2520(HNLC)%252C%2520a%2520banned%2520armed%2Calleged%2520indifference%2520to%2520its%2520demands.%5C%22%3Ewalked%20out%20of%20the%20peace%20talks%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20several%20grounds%20including%20the%20government%20not%20lifting%20the%20ban%20on%20the%20outfit%20and%20also%20not%20closing%20cases%20registered%20against%20their%20leaders.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELymba%E2%80%99s%20arrest%20in%20the%20case%20has%20created%20a%20stir%20in%20some%20circles%20of%20the%20state%2C%20even%20as%20HNYF%20president%20Sadon%20Blah%20met%20Ravi%20on%20Monday%2C%20March%2011%2C%20to%20vouch%20for%20his%20innocence.%20%E2%80%9CLymba%E2%80%99s%20arrest%20is%20unacceptable%20to%20us.%20He%20is%20known%20to%20have%20a%20very%20calm%20demeanour%20and%20would%20not%20engage%20in%20such%20unlawful%20acts%2C%20%E2%80%9C%20Blah%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthemeghalayan.com%2Fhnyf-chief-vouches-for-arrested-member-warns-group-wont-remain-silent-if-proven-innocent%2F%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20reporters%20in%20Shillong.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStating%20that%20the%20organisation%20would%20wait%20for%20the%20police%20investigation%20to%20be%20done%20before%20deciding%20its%20next%20course%20of%20action%2C%20Blah%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20has%20been%20part%20of%20the%20peace%20talks%20right%20from%20picking%20up%20the%20HNLC%20cadres%20from%20Dawki%20(after%20they%20entered%20India%20from%20Bangladesh).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20arrests%20have%20come%20close%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20three%20other%20arrests%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20police%20in%20the%20North%20Garo%20Hills%20district%20on%20March%205%2C%20based%20on%20a%20complaint%20filed%20on%20February%2025%20by%20a%20local%20resident%20about%20having%20received%20a%20demand%20to%20revive%20the%20banned%20outfit%2C%20GNLA.%20The%20demand%20for%20funds%20came%20just%20days%20after%20a%20press%20release%20had%20gone%20viral%20on%20social%20media%20announcing%20the%20revival%20of%20GNLA%20in%20the%20Garo%20hills.%20The%20state%20government%20had%2C%20thereafter%2C%20said%20the%20police%20were%20looking%20into%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGNLA%20was%20widely%20believed%20to%20have%20ceased%20to%20exist%20with%20the%20killing%20of%20its%20top%20leader%20Sohan%20D%20Shira%20in%202018.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20past%20March%205%2C%20Bruno%20A%20Sangma%2C%20the%20North%20Garo%20Hills%20superintendent%20of%20police%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthemeghalayan.com%2Ffund-drive-in-name-of-gnla-revival-hits-police-wall-in-garo-hills%2F%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Meghalayan%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20on%20receiving%20the%20FIR%20regarding%20the%20demand%20for%20money%2C%20the%20district%20police%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Es%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewung%20into%20action%20and%20began%20an%20investigation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20probe%2C%20we%20successfully%20managed%20to%20arrest%20three%20persons%2C%20including%20the%20kingpin%20who%20is%20a%20former%20militant.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710231292000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12133859%2FUntitled-design-35-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fied-blast-in-shillong-amid-fears-of-revival-of-outlawed-armed-outfit%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20IED%20blast%20occurred%20around%2010%3A30%20pm%20on%20March%209%20at%20Harijan%20colony%20in%20Shillong%20which%20has%20been%20in%20the%20news%20regarding%20the%20resistance%20of%20the%20Sikh%20community%20to%20move%20to%20another%20location%20identified%20by%20the%20state%20government.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fied-blast-in-shillong-amid-fears-of-revival-of-outlawed-armed-outfit%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%20Violence%3A%20SC%20Seeks%20Probe%20Status%20from%20State%20Govt%2C%20CBI%2C%20NIA%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F11142639%2FUntitled-design-1-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Monday%2C%20March%2011%2C%20directed%20the%20Manipur%20government%2C%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20and%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA)%20to%20file%20reports%20elaborating%20on%20the%20status%20of%20probe%20and%20the%20charge%20sheets%20filed%20in%20cases%20of%20ethnic%20violence%20to%20help%20it%20take%20a%20decision%20on%20whether%20the%20trials%20can%20commence%20in%20Assam%20or%20be%20undertaken%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20three-judge%20bench%20presided%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20was%20dealing%20with%20a%20communication%20from%20the%20registrar%20general%20of%20Gauhati%20high%20court%20forwarding%20a%20letter%20of%20the%20special%20judge%2C%20CBI%2C%20and%20NIA%2C%20seeking%20clarifications%20on%20whether%20trial%20should%20be%20conducted%20in%20Assam%20after%20the%20filing%20of%20chargesheets%2C%20and%20modalities%20to%20be%20followed%20in%20the%20case%20an%20accused%20is%20found%20to%20be%20juvenile%20on%20the%20date%20of%20commission%20of%20an%20offence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20apex%20court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fmanipur-violence-supreme-court-seeks-probe-status-reports-from-govt-agencies-9208731%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20letter%20of%20the%20Special%20Judge%20arises%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20order%20dated%20August%2025%2C%202023%2C%20of%20this%20court%20by%20which%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20Gauhati%20High%20Court%20was%20requested%20to%20nominate%20one%20or%20more%20officers%20of%20the%20rank%20of%20Chief%20Judicial%20Magistrate%20and%20Special%20Judge%20in%20Gauhati%2C%20Assam%2C%20to%20conduct%20all%20proceedings%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20investigation%20of%20cases%20relating%20to%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur%E2%80%A6.We%20direct%20that%20an%20updated%20status%20report%20be%20filed%E2%80%A6within%20a%20period%20of%20two%20weeks%20by%20the%20government%20of%20Manipur%20as%20well%20as%20CBI%2FNIA%20in%20regard%20to%20the%20investigations.%20The%20status%20report%20shall%20indicate%20whether%20chargesheets%20have%20been%20filed%2C%20and%20if%20so%20in%20how%20many%20cases%20and%20the%20stage%20of%20the%20investigation%20in%20others.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20also%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20it%20cannot%20issue%20directions%20to%20the%20state%20government%20and%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20to%20maintain%20law%20and%20order%20in%20Manipur%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20a%20spate%20of%20violent%20incidents%2C%20armed%20protests%2C%20blocking%20of%20the%20highways%20and%20the%20attack%20on%20the%20residence%20of%20a%20district%20collector%20in%20the%20last%20two%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20are%20the%20matters%20where%20this%20court%20cannot%20give%20directions.%20We%20cannot%20be%20issuing%20directions%20to%20the%20civil%20society%20organisations%20to%20maintain%20law%20and%20order%E2%80%A6The%20state%20government%20is%20there%20to%20maintain%20law%20and%20order%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20bench%20also%20comprising%20Justices%20J.B.%20Pardiwla%20and%20Manoj%20Misra%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fmanipur-violence-supreme-court-seeks-report-from-state-cbi-nia-on-status-of-probe-filing-of-charge-sheets%2Fcid%2F2006217%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20PTI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20told%20attorney%20general%20R.%20Venkataramani%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20Manipur%20government%20and%20the%20investigation%20agencies%2C%20to%20take%20instructions%20on%20the%20report%20of%20the%20Justice%20Gita%20Mittal%20committee%20on%20the%20recent%20incidents%20of%20violence%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20Justice%20Mittal%20committee%20wanted%20the%20top%20court%20to%20pass%20some%20orders%20following%20the%20recent%20incidents%20of%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20asked%20the%20counsel%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20panel%2C%20to%20provide%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20report%20to%20the%20attorney%20general%20to%20take%20instructions%20on%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditional%20solicitor%20general%20Aishwarya%20Bhati%2C%20who%20was%20also%20appeared%20for%20the%20Manipur%20government%2C%20urged%20the%20court%20that%20trial%20be%20held%20in%20the%20state%20as%20there%20was%20a%20marked%20improvement%20in%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20know%20whether%20the%20cases%20were%20ripe%20for%20the%20trial%20or%20not%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20a%20tabulated%20chart%20be%20filed%20on%20the%20status%20of%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20apex%20court%20ordered%20the%20listing%20of%20petitions%20on%20Manipur%20violence%20after%20two%20weeks.%20The%20top%20court%20had%2C%20on%20August%2025%20last%20year%2C%20ordered%20transfer%20of%20several%20Manipur%20violence%20cases%20being%20probed%20by%20the%20CBI%2C%20including%20the%20sexual%20assault%20case%20of%20two%20women%20seen%20in%20a%20viral%20video%20being%20paraded%20naked%2C%20to%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20asked%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20the%20Gauhati%20high%20court%20to%20nominate%20one%20or%20more%20judicial%20officers%20to%20deal%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20several%20directions%2C%20the%20apex%20court%20ordered%20virtual%20examination%20of%20victims%20and%20witnesses%20by%20courts%2C%20saying%20they%20have%20been%20issued%20%E2%80%9Cat%20the%20present%20stage%2C%20bearing%20in%20mind%20the%20overall%20environment%20in%20Manipur%20and%20the%20need%20for%20ensuring%20a%20fair%20process%20of%20criminal%20justice%20administration%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBoth%20sides%20(Kuki%20and%20Meiteis)%20have%20been%20hurt%20%E2%80%A6There%20have%20been%20victims%20in%20valleys%2C%20and%20in%20hills.%20It%20would%20be%20difficult%20for%20people%20who%20suffered%20in%20valleys%20to%20travel%20to%20hills%2C%20and%20the%20other%20way%20round.%20We%20are%20not%20on%20who%20suffered%20more%2C%20just%20the%20practical%20difficulty%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20CJI%20had%20said%2C%20adding%20the%20top%20court%20will%20pass%20orders%20which%20will%20be%20fair%20to%20both%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20this%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20had%20ordered%20a%20CBI%20probe%20into%20several%20cases%20of%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710231256000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F11142639%2FUntitled-design-1-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmanipur-violence-sc-seeks-probe-status-from-state-govt-cbi-nia%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Based%20on%20the%20reports%20on%20status%20of%20probe%20and%20filing%20of%20chargesheets%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20it%20will%20take%20a%20call%20on%20whether%20the%20trials%20can%20commence%20in%20Assam%20or%20be%20undertaken%20in%20Manipur%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmanipur-violence-sc-seeks-probe-status-from-state-govt-cbi-nia%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia%20arrests%20S%20Korean%20man%20on%20spying%20charges%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710231014000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FD582%2Fproduction%2F_132885645_gettyimages-102701759.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-68541185%231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Korean%20media%20report%20the%20man%20is%20a%20religious%20worker%20who%20was%20detained%20in%20January%20in%20Russ