erstar%20Vijay%20Calls%20Citizenship%20Law%20CAA%20%26quot%3BUnacceptable%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECAA%20Rules%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETamil%20superstar%20Vijay%20on%20Monday%20called%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%20%26quot%3Bunacceptable%26quot%3B%20and%20called%20on%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%20to%20not%20allow%20its%20implementation%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fsearch%3Fsearchtext%3DCAA%5C%22%3ECAA%3C%2Fa%3E%20aims%20to%20grant%20citizenship%20to%20persecuted%20minorities%20from%20three%20neighbouring%20countries.%20The%20law%20came%20into%20effect%20yesterday%20following%20a%20gazette%20notification%20by%20the%20central%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijay%2C%20who%20announced%20a%20new%20political%20party%20Tamizha%20Vetri%20Kazhagam%20last%20month%2C%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release%20that%20the%20CAA%20is%20being%20implemented%20due%20to%20%26quot%3Bdivisive%20politics%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22qme%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FCitizenshipAmendmentAct%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23CitizenshipAmendmentAct%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F4iO2VqQnv4%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F4iO2VqQnv4%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20TVK%20Vijay%20(%40tvkvijayhq)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftvkvijayhq%2Fstatus%2F1767241944932237340%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2011%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20law%20like%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%2C%202019%20is%20not%20acceptable%20in%20an%20environment%20where%20citizens%20of%20the%20country%20live%20with%20social%20harmony.%20The%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%20must%20assure%20that%20they%20will%20not%20implement%20the%20law%20in%20the%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn