nance-minister%2Farticleshow%2F108421371.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fex-jp-morgan-banker-muhammad-aurangzeb-becomes-pakistans-new-finance-minister%2Famp_articleshow%2F108421371.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fex-jp-morgan-banker-muhammad-aurangzeb-becomes-pakistans-new-finance-minister%2Famp_articleshow%2F108421371.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Making%20Sense%20of%20the%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20Lok%20Sabha%20Candidate%20List%26nbsp%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12101710%2FGITMKbFXgAAZd18.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKolkata%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Eight%20sitting%20MLAs%20including%20two%20ministers%2C%20one%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%2C%20and%20three%20MLAs%20who%20won%20on%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20tickets%2C%20have%20found%20their%20places%20in%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20(TMC%E2%80%99s)%20list%20of%20candidates%20for%20the%2042%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20faces%20in%20the%20list%20include%20cricketer-turned-former%20BJP%20MP%20Kirti%20Azad%20in%20the%20constituency%20currently%20held%20by%20BJP%20veteran%20Surinder%20Singh%20Ahluwalia%2C%20former%20cricketer%20Yusuf%20Pathan%20against%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Lok%20Sabha%20leader%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%2C%20and%20actor-cum-reality%20show%20host%20Rachana%20Banerjee%20against%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20sitting%20MP%2C%20former%20actor%20Locket%20Chatterjee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20the%20TMC%20won%2022%20seats%2C%20while%20the%20BJP%20won%2018%20and%20the%20Congress%20won%20two.%20Later%2C%20two%20MPs%2C%20the%20father%20and%20brother%20of%20rebel%20TMC%20leader%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%20who%20is%20now%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%2C%20allied%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20though%20without%20formally%20joining%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20BJP%20MP%20Arjun%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20originally%20from%20the%20TMC%2C%20switched%20back%20to%20the%20TMC%20in%202022.%20The%20party%20also%20wrested%20Asansol%20Lok%20Sabha%20from%20the%20BJP%20in%20a%202021%20bypoll%20after%20MP%20Babul%20Supriyo%20resigned%20and%20joined%20the%20TMC.%20This%20left%20the%20TMC%20effectively%20with%2022%20MPs%20and%20the%20BJP%20with%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%2C%20as%20of%20now%2C%20named%C2%A020%20candidates%2C%20of%20whom%20the%20Asansol%20nominee%2C%20Bhojpuri%20singer%20Pawan%20Singh%2C%20subsequently%20declined.%20The%20party%20has%20renominated%20nine%20incumbent%20MPs%2C%20including%20three%20junior%20Union%20ministers%2C%20and%20fielded%20three%20sitting%20MLAs.%C2%A0The%20Left%20parties%20and%20the%20Congress%20are%20yet%20to%20announce%20any%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TMC%2C%20among%20its%20sitting%20MPs%2C%20has%20dropped%20six.%20They%20are%20actors%20Nusrat%20Jahan%20(Basirhat)%20and%20Mimi%20Chakraborty%20(Jadavpur)%20and%20district-level%20leaders%20Sunil%20Mandal%20(Bardhaman%20Purba)%2C%20Aparupa%20Poddar%20(Arambag)%20and%20C.M.%20Jatua%20(Mathurapur).%20Arjun%20Singh%20(Barrackpore)%2C%20too%2C%20failed%20to%20find%20favour%20with%20the%20party%20despite%20coming%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20octogenarian%20Jatua%20is%20not%20contesting%20due%20to%20his%20advanced%20age%2C%20the%20rest%20were%20dropped%20apparently%20because%20the%20party%20was%20not%20satisfied%20with%20their%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsumer%20affairs%20minister%20Biplab%20Mitra%20has%20been%20fielded%20from%20Balurghat%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%20has%20renominated%20the%20incumbent%20MP%2C%20state%20unit%20president%20Sukanta%20Majumdar.%20Irrigation%20and%20waterways%20minister%20Partha%20Bhowmik%20has%20been%20fielded%20from%20Barrackpore%2C%20the%20seat%20that%20Arjun%20Singh%20wrested%20from%20the%20TMC%20contesting%20on%20a%20BJP%20ticket%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20sitting%20MLAs%2C%20Bongaon%20MLA%20Biswajit%20Das%2C%20Raiganj%20MLA%20Krishna%20Kalyani%20and%20Ranaghat%20Dakshin%20MLA%20Mukut%20Mani%20Adhikari%20won%20on%20BJP%20tickets%20in%202021%20but%20later%20joined%20the%20TMC.%20None%20of%20them%20has%20resigned%20to%20date%2C%20while%20Kalyani%20is%20also%20the%20TMC-backed%20chairman%20of%20the%20public%20accounts%20committee%20in%20the%20state%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDas%20will%20be%20facing%20junior%20shipping%20minister%20Shantanu%20Thakur%20in%20Bongaon%2C%20while%20Kalyani%20has%20been%20fielded%20from%20former%20junior%20Union%20minister%20Debashree%20Chaudhuri%E2%80%99s%20Raiganj%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat.%20The%20BJP%20is%20yet%20to%20name%20its%20candidate.%20Adhikari%2C%20a%20leader%20of%20the%20Matua-Namashudra%20community%2C%20has%20been%20pitted%20against%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Jagannath%20Sarkar%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20incumbent%20in%20the%20Matua-dominated%20Ranaghat%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20MLAs%20will%20now%20have%20to%20resign%20%E2%80%93%20as%20they%20are%20contesting%20on%20a%20different%20party%E2%80%99s%20ticket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20sitting%20TMC%20MLAs%2C%20Sitai%20MLA%20Jagadish%20Chandra%20Basunia%20has%20been%20fielded%20against%20junior%20home%20minister%20Nishith%20Paramanik%20in%20Cooch%20Behar%2C%20and%20actor-turned-Medinipur%20MLA%20June%20Malia%20has%20been%20fielded%20from%20Medinipur%2C%20which%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20former%20state%20unit%20president%20Dilip%20Ghosh%20won%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22As%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20Lies%20Low%2C%20Rumours%20Rife%20on%20Aunt-Nephew%20Tension%20Within%20TMC%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fas-abhishek-banerjee-lays-low-rumours-rife-on-aunt-nephew-tension-within-tmc%5C%22%3EAs%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20Lies%20Low%2C%20Rumours%20Rife%20on%20Aunt-Nephew%20Tension%20Within%20TMC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatashpur%20MLA%20Uttam%20Barik%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20sabhadhipati%20(chairperson)%20of%20East%20Midnapore%20zilla%20parishad%20(district%20council)%2C%20has%20been%20fielded%20against%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%E2%80%99s%20brother%2C%20Soumyendu%2C%20from%20Kanthi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBasirhat%20MLA%20Haji%20Nurul%20Islam%2C%20who%20was%20earlier%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20Basirhat%20MP%2C%20has%20been%20fielded%20again%20from%20Basirhat%20Lok%20Sabha.%20Balarampur%20MLA%20and%20former%20state%20minister%20Shantiram%20Mahato%20has%20been%20fielded%20against%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Purulia%20incumbent%20Jagannath%20Singh%20Mahato%2C%20Taldangra%20MLA%20and%20TMC%20Bankura%20district%20unit%20president%20has%20been%20fielded%20against%20Union%20minister%20Sarkar%20in%20Bankura%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20and%20Dhupguri%20MLA%20Nirmal%20Chandra%20Roy%20from%20BJP-held%20Jalpaiguri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajya%20Sabha%20member%20Prakash%20Chik%20Baraik%20is%20contesting%20from%20the%20tribal-dominated%20Alipurduar%2C%20the%20constituency%20of%20outgoing%20junior%20Union%20minister%20John%20Barla%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%20has%20now%20fielded%20two-time%20MLA%20Manoj%20Tigga.%20Baraik%20was%20elected%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20only%20in%20August%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20new%20faces%2C%20a%20prominent%20one%20is%20youth%20leader%20and%20spokesperson%20Debangshu%20Bhattacharya%20from%20Tamluk%2C%20where%20the%20incumbent%20MP%20is%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%E2%80%99s%20brother%2C%20Dibyendu.%20Most%20BJP%20leaders%20in%20West%20Bengal%20expect%20former%20Calcutta%20high%20court%20judge%20Abhijit%20Gangopadhyay%2C%20who%20recently%20joined%20the%20BJP%2C%20to%20be%20fielded%20from%20Tamluk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20veteran%20MPs%20who%20have%20won%20three%20or%20more%20times%2C%20Sougata%20Roy%2C%20Sudeep%20Bandyopadhyay%2C%20Kalyan%20Bandyopadhyay%2C%20Kakoli%20Ghosh%20Dastidar%20and%20Shatabdi%20Roy%20have%20been%20renominated%20from%20Dumdum%2C%20Kolkata%20North%2C%20Shreerampore%2C%20Barasat%20and%20Birbhum%2C%20respectively.%20The%20party%20chief%E2%80%99s%20nephew%20and%20the%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20all-India%20general%20secretary%20and%20two-time%20Diamond%20Harbour%20MP%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20will%20be%20contesting%20from%20his%20home%20turf.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20has%20expectedly%20renominated%20Mahua%20Moitra%2C%20the%20outspoken%20Krishnanagar%20MP%20and%20staunch%20BJP%20critic%2C%20who%20was%20expelled%20from%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%20December%20last%20year%20in%20a%20controversial%20chain%20of%20events.%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20had%20earlier%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20she%20was%20standing%20by%20Moitra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20has%20also%20renominated%20two-time%20MPs%2C%20former%20footballer%20Prasun%20Banerjee%20and%20actor%20Dipak%20Adhikary%20AKA%20Dev%2C%20and%20Pratima%20Mandal%2C%20and%20one-time%20MPs%20Asit%20Mal%2C%20Sajda%20Ahmed%2C%20Khalilur%20Rahman%20and%20Abu%20Taher%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDeciphering%20the%20message%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0on%20condition%20of%20anonymity%2C%20some%20TMC%20leaders%20described%20the%20list%20as%20%E2%80%9Ca%20perfect%20example%20of%20striking%20a%20balance%20between%20all%20interests%E2%80%9D%2C%20while%20some%20others%20said%20it%20reflected%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Clack%20of%20confidence%20and%20strategy%20confusion.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERather%20strangely%2C%20there%20is%20a%20notable%20drop%20in%20the%20number%20of%20women%20candidates.%20From%2017%20candidates%20in%202019%2C%20it%20has%20come%20down%20to%2012%20this%20time.%20This%20is%20despite%20the%20party%2C%20over%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20repeatedly%20taking%20pride%20in%20giving%2040%25%20of%20nominations%20to%20women%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20The%20party%20also%20focuses%20on%20women%20as%20one%20of%20its%20core%20support%20bases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20the%20party%20is%20looking%20to%20improve%20its%20tally%20by%20consolidating%20Muslim%20votes%20in%20its%20favour%2C%20the%20number%20of%20Muslim%20candidates%20has%20also%20dropped%20from%20seven%20in%202019%20to%20six%20this%20time.%20More%20than%20one-fourth%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20population%20is%20Muslim%2C%20according%20to%20the%20census%20of%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20fielding%20three%20candidates%20who%20are%20from%20outside%20the%20state%20%E2%80%93%20sitting%20Asansol%20MP%20former%20actor%20Shatrughan%20Sinha%2C%20Kirti%20Azad%20from%20Bardhaman-Durgapur%20and%20Yousuf%20Pathan%20from%20Baharampur%20%E2%80%93%20has%20left%20many%20TMC%20leaders%20and%20workers%20confused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20ruling%20party%2C%20chief%20minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%E2%80%99s%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%2C%20has%20repeatedly%20branded%20the%20BJP%20as%20an%20%E2%80%9Coutsider%E2%80%9D%20force%2C%20which%20culminated%20in%20their%202021%20assembly%20election%20campaign%20theme%C2%A0%3Cem%3EBangla%20Nijer%20Meyeke%20Chay%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(Bengal%20wants%20it%20own%20daughter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESinha%20and%20Azad%20hail%20from%20Bihar%20and%20were%20former%20BJP%20MPs%20from%20there%2C%20while%20Pathan%20is%20from%20PM%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20home%20state%20of%20Gujarat.%20The%20TMC%2C%20though%2C%20highlighted%20Pathan%E2%80%99s%20Bengal%20connection%20as%20one%20who%20played%20for%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20(KKR)%20in%20the%20IPL%20cricket%20league.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20these%20announcements%2C%20several%20district-level%20TMC%20leaders%20whom%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0spoke%20to%20said%20they%20were%20apprehensive%20it%20could%20blunt%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20Bengali%20ethnic%20identity%20plank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Maidul%20Islam%2C%20a%20political%20scientist%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20Studies%20in%20Social%20Sciences%2C%20Calcutta%20(CSSSC)%2C%20the%20TMC%20chose%20to%20play%20safe%20by%20nominating%20tested%20politicians%20with%20a%20history%20of%20electoral%20success%20and%20reducing%20celebrity%20dependence%2C%20but%20two%20celebrity%20candidates%20from%20outside%20the%20state%20may%20blunt%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Coutsider%20versus%20daughter%20of%20the%20soil%E2%80%9D%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20can%20understand%20re-nominating%20Sinha.%20He%20is%20already%20the%20sitting%20MP%20and%20Asansol%20has%20a%20significant%20Hindi-speaking%20population.%20Bardhaman-Durgapur%20also%20has%20some%20Hindi%20speaking%20population%20but%20the%20candidature%20of%20Azad%20and%20Pathan%20would%20contradict%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20appeal%20towards%20Bengali%20ethnic%20sentiments%20and%20anti-outsider%20pitch%2C%E2%80%9D%20Islam%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22There%E2%80%99s%20Temple%20Politics%20Where%20You%20Least%20Expect%20It%20%E2%80%93%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20Jungle%20Mahal%2C%20for%20One%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftheres-temple-politics-where-you-least-expect-it-bengals-jungle-mahal-for-one%5C%22%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20Temple%20Politics%20Where%20You%20Least%20Expect%20It%20%E2%80%93%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20Jungle%20Mahal%2C%20for%20One%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20the%20names%20were%20announced%2C%20Bengal%20Congress%20president%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20took%20potshots%20at%20the%20TMC%20for%20%E2%80%9Cimporting%20candidates%E2%80%9D%2C%20asking%20why%20the%20TMC%20could%20not%20find%20suitable%20candidates%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20BJP%20state%20unit%20president%20Sukanta%20Majumdar%20asked%20whether%20Sinha%2C%20Azad%20and%20Pathan%20would%20be%20called%20%E2%80%9Coutsiders%E2%80%9D%20in%20Bengal%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20political%20analyst%20Udayan%20Bandyopadhyay%2C%20an%20associate%20professor%20at%20Bangabasi%20College%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20considers%20the%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20list%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9Cmore%20reflective%20of%20inclusive%20politics%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20think%20the%20inclusive%20pitch%20is%20better%20than%20the%20anti-outsider%20pitch%2C%20which%20is%20more%20of%20an%20exclusionary%20nature.%20Sinha%2C%20Azad%20and%20Pathan%E2%80%99s%20candidature%20also%20reflects%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20desire%20to%20have%20prominent%20faces%20addressing%20the%20audience%20outside%20West%20Bengal%2C%20on%20issues%20of%20national%20significance%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bandyopadhyay%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBandyopadhyay%20agrees%20that%20fielding%20so%20many%20sitting%20MLAs%20also%20reflected%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20fear%20and%20lack%20of%20confidence.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Jalpaiguri%20candidate%2C%20Nirmal%20Chandra%20Roy%2C%20had%20only%20just%20won%20the%20Dhupduri%20assembly%20by-election.%20He%20has%20a%20good%20image%20but%20he%20could%20also%20be%20a%20leading%20face%20in%20the%20campaign%20while%20the%20party%20fielded%20someone%20else%20to%20contest%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20The%20candidature%20is%20reflective%20of%20how%20limited%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20options%20were%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20other%20fresh%20candidates%20are%20TMC%20youth%20wing%E2%80%99s%20state%20unit%20president%20Sayoni%20Ghosh%20from%20Jadavpur%2C%20Sundarban%20district%20youth%20wing%20president%20Bapi%20Haldar%20from%20Mathurapur%2C%20Hooghly%20Zilla%20Parishad%20member%20Malati%20Bag%20from%20Arambagh%2C%20Santali%20literature%20and%20Padmashree%20and%20Banga%20Bibhushan%20awardee%20Kalipada%20Soren%20from%20Jhargram%2C%20psychiatrist%20Sharmila%20Sarkar%20from%20Bardhaman%20Purba%20and%20ex%20IPS%20Prasun%20Bandyopadhyay%20from%20Malda%20Uttar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp