0kmph%2C%20nothing%20will%20happen%20to%20the%20rooftop%20solar%20structure%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSee%2C%20these%20solar%20installations%20are%20subject%20to%20external%20weather%2C%20elevated%2C%20and%20on%20top%20of%20a%20roof%2C%20and%20subject%20to%20high%20wind%20speed%20pressure.%20They%20have%20to%20be%20durable.%20We%20install%20our%20solar%20kit%20in%20just%20six%20to%20seven%20hours.%20Once%20installed%2C%20the%20customer%20requires%20an%20inspection%20from%20their%20local%20power%20discom.%20Once%20the%20site%20is%20inspected%2C%20their%20final%20bank%20details%20are%20uploaded%20on%20the%20Government%20portal%20and%20the%20subsidy%20comes%20into%20their%20bank%20account%20within%20just%2030%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Nikhil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Government%20recently%20launched%20the%20National%20Portal%20for%20Rooftop%20Solar%20on%20the%20back%20of%20which%20all%20of%20these%20Government%20subsidies%20and%20applications%20are%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20take%20care%20of%20all%20these%20applications%20for%20the%20consumer.%20We%20take%20care%20of%20Government%20permits%2C%20subsidy%20applications%2C%20EMI%20applications%2C%20inspections%2C%20design%2C%20procurement%2C%20etc.%20We%20are%20a%20full-stacked%20brand%20that%20offers%20end-to-end%20solutions%20for%20the%20Indian%20consumer%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shreya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20installation%20comes%20the%20most%20important%20part%20%E2%80%94%20after-sale%20service.%20India%20is%20a%20country%20where%20roofs%20are%20subject%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20dust%20and%20a%20variety%20of%20external%20weather%20conditions.%20These%20elements%20cause%20a%20lot%20of%20wear%20and%20tear%20on%20rooftop%20solar%20panels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20offer%20a%20five-year%20comprehensive%20solar%20care%20plan%20in%20which%20we%20take%20care%20of%20everything%20from%20panel%20deep%20cleaning%20to%20technical%2C%20mechanical%2C%20and%20electrical%20maintenance.%20Once%20installed%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20your%20roof%20and%20solar%20energy%20but%20our%20responsibility.%20As%20a%20policy%2C%20we%20sell%20a%20five-year%20comprehensive%20solar%20care%20plan%20so%20that%20consumers%20can%20enjoy%20the%20benefits%20of%20zero-electricity%20bills%20year%20after%20year.%20Consumers%20can%20renew%20their%20after-sale%20care%20plan%20with%20us%20after%20these%20five%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Neeraj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20look%20at%20rooftop%20solar%20systems%20as%20an%20investment%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20seeing%2020-25%25%20IRR%20(internal%20rate%20of%20return)%20if%20it%20gives%20you%20the%20right%20performance.%20Maintenance%20is%20important%20because%20that%E2%80%99s%20how%20you%20realise%20that%2020-25%25%20IRR.%20Every%20month%20or%20three%20months%2C%20a%20trained%20SolarSquare%20technician%20will%20come%20to%20your%20home%2C%20do%20a%20complete%20technical%20check%2C%20electrical%20maintenance%2C%20and%20mechanical%20check%2C%20and%20do%20a%20deep%20cleaning%20of%20the%20solar%20panels%20to%20ensure%20any%20hard%20dust%20or%20bird%20droppings%20are%20removed.%20Following%20this%20check%2C%20you%20will%20see%20a%20spike%20in%20power%20production%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Shreya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Rooftop-Solar-1709904626.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Achieve%20zero%20electricity%20bills%20with%20solar%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Rooftop-Solar-1709904626.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Rooftop-Solar-1709904626-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Rooftop-Solar-1709