e%20will%20have%20to%20devise%20comprehensive%20plans%20to%20recycle%20decommissioned%20panels.%20%E2%80%9CSince%20we%20are%20only%20a%20nine-year-old%20company%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20solar%20installations%20that%20have%20reached%20the%20end%20of%20life.%20The%20question%20of%20disposal%20and%20recycling%20is%20important.%20Thankfully%2C%20you%20already%20have%20companies%20in%20the%20US%20that%20can%20recycle%2070%25%20of%20the%20components%20and%20materials%20used%20to%20make%20solar%20panels%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20a%20team%20of%20researchers%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20Sustainable%20Technologies%20(CST)%2C%20led%20by%20Dr%20Monto%20Mani%20and%20operating%20out%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F287506%2Fiisc-bengaluru-reuse-upcycle-old-decommissioned-solar-panels-as-building-material%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20Institute%20of%20Science%20(IISc)%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20Bengaluru%2C%20is%20exploring%20whether%20old%20discarded%20solar%20panels%20can%20be%20upcycled%20as%20a%20building%20material.%20With%20this%2C%20they%20are%20looking%20to%20extend%20the%20panels%E2%80%99%20useful%20life%20by%20a%20few%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20their%20future%20as%20a%20business%2C%20things%20look%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202021%2C%20they%20raised%20Rs%2030%20crore%20in%20their%20Seed%20round.%20During%20their%20Series%20A%20round%20in%20October%202022%2C%20they%20raised%20Rs%20100%20crore.%20%E2%80%9CLower%20Carbon%2C%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20climate%20tech%20funds%2C%20is%20our%20shareholder.%20It%20was%20their%20first%20investment%20in%20India.%20We%20also%20have%20Elevation%20Capital%2C%20who%20are%20investors%20in%20Swiggy%20and%20Urban%20Company%2C%20and%20other%20notable%20investors%20on%20board%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20according%20to%20a%20November%202023%20report%20by%20the%20Council%20on%20Energy%2C%20Environment%20and%20Water%20(CEEW)%2C%20more%20than%2025%20crore%20households%20in%20India%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20deploy%20637%20GW%20of%20solar%20energy%20capacity%20on%20rooftops.%20According%20to%20a%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%20report%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20the%20same%2C%20%E2%80%9CFurther%2C%20the%20CEEW%20report%20found%20that%20deploying%20just%20one-third%20of%20this%20total%20solar%20technical%20potential%20could%20support%20the%20entire%20electricity%20demand%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20residential%20sector%20(~310%20TWh).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20ventures%20like%20SolarSquare%2C%20the%20opportunities%20are%20massive%20and%20the%20future%20looks%20promising.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20SolarSquare)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHomeowner%E2%80%99s%20Guide%20to%20Buying%20Rooftop%20Solar%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.solarsquare.in%2Ffill-download-form%3Futm_source%3DPR%26utm_medium%3DOrganic%26utm_campaign%3DTheBetterIndia08032024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESolarSquare%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98SolarSquare%E2%80%99s%20co-founders%20on%20the%20%2450%20billion%20opportunity%20to%20bring%20solar%20power%20to%20Indian%20homes%E2%80%99%20by%20Harichandran%20Arakali%3B%20Published%20on%2014%20June%202022%20courtesy%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbesindia.com%2Faudio%2Fforbes-india-daily-tech-conver-sation%2Fsolarsquares-cofounders-on-the-50-billion-opportunity-to-bring-solar-power-to-indian-homes%2F77269%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EForbes